(1, 80, 'Surya', 'surya', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Sun popularly known as Surya in Vedic Astrology is the king of all planets. It is the karaka for soul which is considered a part of God or God itselt. Not only that Surya is responsible for health, fame and leadership roles. Surya is also a karaka for father. Our eyes which let us see this beautiful world are governed by Surya as well. It is a male planet, royalty in nature and is given the title of King among planets.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Surya is the king and leadership skills come naturally to those with good placement for Surya, ideally the 10th house. Many great politicians and leaders have Surya in an important placement in the horoscope. People with positive Surya in a horoscope show poise, confidence and firm determination. They rise to the status of a leader and an able administrator. People with a good Surya can be quite successful in the areas of agriculture and administration. Goverment jobs which provide a sense of security and stability are very likely due to a good Surya in a horoscope. Even if Surya is in <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=28:tula&amp;catid=11:12-signs&amp;Itemid=111">libra</a> which is its neecha rashi, provided it causes a neecha bhanga you are sure to see the concerned individual in a very important administrative or political role. Bear in mind they rarely get the top position if Surya is indeed in libra. Health, Vigour and Vitality all improve if Surya is in a good placement in a horoscope. With Budh as a co-tenant in a good sign or house, a very powerful yoga called Budh-Adidya Yoga is formed. It provides wealth, fame and prosperity.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;There are downsides to any planet and Surya is no different. While a positive sun is a boon for individuals it is a curse for those around him. Surya is arrogant and inconsiderate to other people''s needs. In popular stories Surya is the father and <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=7:shani&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Shani</a> is the son yet they both don''t get along well. This is partly down to the autocratic and dictatorial nature of Surya the father and unapologetic and rigid nature of Shani the son. Families where father and children don''t get along well are sure to have Surya-Shani relationship in one way or the other. Surya influenced people generally get high positions and they are sure to push everyone to work beyond their possible limit which maybe fortunate for the enterprises but not so fortunate for the employees. Well surely they don''t become Mr. Popular with the minions yet they are sure to get special accolades from their bosses. In terms of health a bad placement of Surya is sure to give you several ailments, weak body and low confidence but a strong placement gives over-confidence in ones abilities and ultimately that causes their downfall. Burns and Boils also happen if Surya is in a fiery sign.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; The problem with people who have a good Surya is they act confident and ambitious and shine a little too much for others to feel jealousy and insecurity. People often confuse their confidence for arrogance and their ambitions for egocentric behavior. They do not help their own cause either by being insensitive to those less confident and successful souls. &nbsp;Not everyone can become successful in life cause if everyone becomes a king then who will be the subjects? This trivial matter is too hard for people with good placement of Surya to understand. While the benefits of a good Surya are great as it gives authority, fame and health one must care not to be over-confident and forget kindness and empathy.</p>', '', 1, 10, '2014-02-01 11:43:52', 899, '', '2014-03-06 06:53:36', 899, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-02-01 11:43:52', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 3, 9, 'surya in astrology, surya in vedic astrology, surya in 12 rashi, surya in 12 bhava', 'Surya in Vedic Astrology', 1, 14, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(2, 82, 'Chandra', 'chandra', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Moon popularly known as Chandra in Vedic Astrology is the planet of affections and emotions. It is a karaka for mind and everything related to it. Moon also affects the blood circulation as well as water portions on the body and on earth. Well that implies nearly 70% of body and of earth are affected by Chandra. Chandra maybe a small planet and it only stays in a rashi for 2.5 days but its implications are huge when you take the co-tenants, rashi and house lords into consideration. Chandra brings tides and ebbs in an ocean and similarly it brings tides and ebbs in a human mind also. Every positive or negative, good or evil, happy or sad, nice or bad thought that comes to an individual is thanks to chandra and associations and afflictions to chandra.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Moon is the closest planet to the earth. Theoretically it is a satellite. Just like satellites are responsible for good and bad signals in a television; Chandra is responsible for good and bad thoughts in an individual. <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=7:shani&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Shani</a> and <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=8:rahu&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Rahu</a> association with Chandra is a prime factor for people with weak or malefic thought process. Of course the rashi occupied by Chandra also plays an important role in shaping the thought process of an individual. Generally speaking association of Chandra to Shani, Rahu, <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=3:mangal&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Mangal</a>, <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=4:buddh&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Budh</a>, <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=1:surya&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Surya</a> and <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=9:ketu&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Ketu</a> is considered bad. Though bear in mind it is not always the case.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Chandra is highly impressionable graha. It quickly takes in the qualities of its rashi, co-tenants and grahas which aspect it.&nbsp;Lets talk in more detail about Chandra and associations with other planets.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Chandra''s association with Surya is called as Amavasya or No Moon. Many astrologers and jyotishis push the panic button once they hear of this scenario. Various havans, poojas and rings are provided to calm these so called horrible scenario. Well the truth couldn''t be farther off. Well Surya is soul and Chandra is the mind and it wouldn''t be so bad if soul and mind become one considering that soul is considered part of god and mind is the most definiting part in an invidual.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Chandra''s association with Mangal is considered auspicious by many astrologers cause it gives abundant wealth. That is partly true but they forget to mention that this association gives rise to a wounded warrior who is always there to take revenge on others.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Chandra''s association with Budh is probably among the worst. Most mental disorders are caused by this association. Chandra controls the mind while Budh takes care of nervous system. Not to mention this association causes an individual to be a chatter box.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Chandra''s association to Guru is probably the best. In a favourable rashi it causes a powerful yoga called Gaja Kesari yoga. It gives abundant wealth, happiness and prosperity.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Chandra''s association with Shukra is also good. It provides abundant love. Most of the romeo-juliet stories are thanks to Chandra-Shukra association. The fairest and most beautiful looking individuals both male and female are very likely to have assocation of Chandra with Shukra.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Chandra''s association with Shani causes Vish Yoga. The mind is constantly in thinking process and nothing comes out of tireless thinking but sadness and worries. Depression is one of the possible scenarious with Shani-Chandra association. But people who learn to control their emotions and adapt to difficulties and changing scenarios become great individuals but that doesn''t come without a struggle.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Chandra with Rahu is bad in general terms. Rahu is cloudy and smokey and causes disruption to natural though process. Simply speaking this association clouds judgement of an individual.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Chandra''s association with Ketu is bad for some and good for some. Ketu is the planet of detachment. Well for those who want to get closer to the god; this placement provides the right tools of obtaining that goal. For those who are too caught up with materialistic success; consider this placement to quite a bother and probably arrange for some counter measures.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Chandra is very small but its implications on human beings are pretty big. It alone is a gentle, calm and caring graha but depending on rashi lordship or co-tenants it could bring peace or havoc in your life. The greatest enemy or friend of an individual is not anyone but his mind and thoughts. Once you control your own mind; controlling this world is not that difficult.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '', 1, 10, '2014-02-01 11:44:20', 899, '', '2014-03-19 07:48:24', 899, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-02-01 11:44:20', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 5, 8, 'chandra in vedic astrology, chandra in astrology, chandra in 12 bhava, chandra in 12 rashi', 'chandra in vedic astrology', 1, 18, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(3, 84, 'Mangal', 'mangal', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Mars popularly known as Mangal is another planet along with Shani who invokes fear in the minds of people especially for those who are of the age where marriage takes priority. A Mangal Dosha is a tragedy for the bride/groom and their parents yet a boon for the astrologers. No one is bothered to know that the very word "Mangal" means good and auspicious. Ofcourse mars is a fiery planet and has his sort of problems associated with itself but it is better to understand why this fiery planet is so angry and cold before making any judgement on people who are influenced very highly by this planet.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Mangal is considered a male planet. To be more precise people born under the infuence of mars are the macho types. These includes females also. The ladies who like to order, shout and get angry to get things done are mostly under the influence of a strong mars in horoscope. Mars has a lot of high octane energy. People under the influence of Mars keep on doing relentless work, want everything on time, get angry at smallest inaccuracies of co-workers or employees and worst of all keep others on their toes. Mars hates laziness and lies. These are the reasons why they are the ideal employees but not-so great employers. Mangal is least likely to cause downfall of others. They may get angry, make enemies, use harsh speech but they rarely ever keep enemity for lives. They may get angry very fast but their anger also calms down after some time. But none the less Mangal does have its share of handicaps.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; Mangal is impatient and very harsh in speech. People under influence of Mars often make rash decisions and make enemies out of people due to their high moral values and principles. The world is not so honest and sincere. It is full of scums and leeches who thrive on looting and cheating others. Since Mangal cannot stand these things he is always at logger-heads with these people. A bride or groom who has Mangal in a prominent position cannot compromise on his/her ideals and principles. That is why a lot of quarrels happen and eventually divorces happen. Ofcourse astrologers do not help the cause by matching partners with Mars or <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=7:shani&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Shani</a>&nbsp;in a prominent position of the partner.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; None the less Mars does have its good side. Mars influence people easily sacrifice their own goodwill for people for whom they care. They would give up their profit for others to avoid loss. If any sort of association with Jupiter is present they could even bear loss if those they care for are profited from their sacrifice.&nbsp;Most of the prominent actors, sportsperson, celebrities and good army commanders have Mars in a very good position. Mars influence people do great in places where everything needs to be done on time like railways and armies. They make very competent lawyers and deal makers.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; In my view some people are born for the benefit of the community. They are there to make a difference. Mars influenced people are one of them. They may not be the most charming people to stay around but they are the most trustworthy, hard working and kind hearted people to be friends with.&nbsp;</p>', '', 1, 10, '2014-02-01 11:45:23', 899, '', '2014-03-06 07:59:59', 899, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-02-01 11:45:23', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"