(37, 152, 'Rohini', 'rohini', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Rohini is the fourth nakshatra among the <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=category&amp;id=12&amp;Itemid=112">27 Nakshatras</a> studied in Vedic Astrology. The gana of Rohini is human and all the 4 Padas of Rohini are in <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=23:vrishabha&amp;catid=11:12-signs&amp;Itemid=111">Vrishabha</a>. Rohini is ruled by <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=2:chandra&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Chandra</a> and the presiding deity is Brahma who is the creator of the Universe. Rohini is symbolized by a chariot pulled by two oxen. In Vedic Texts it is mentioned that Rohini was the most favorite wife of Chandra among the 27 nakshatras (all married to Chandra) and Chandra''s impartial love towards Rohini and neglecting of other wives led Daksha Prajapati to curse Chandra.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Physical Attributes: Both males and females natives of Rohini have attractive eyes and graceful appearance. Males have a slender physique and females have a fair complexion. They are loved and honored due to their charming personality.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Character &amp; Events: Rohini is ruled by Chandra and located in Vrishabha which is a rashi ruled by <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=6:shukra&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Shukra</a>. Naturally the Rohini natives are emotional and attracted to finer things in life. They are highly imaginative and lovers or art, music, dance and sculptures. They have a charming and attractive personality yet can be quite stubborn at times. Generally both males and females are very sensitive and extra caution is advised when dealing with them. Rohini natives have a restless mind and keeping focus on a single activity is next to impossible for them. Rohini natives think with their hearts and not with their heads. This is why they can be easily manipulated. Females are well dressed and well behaved but often short tempered and violent when instigated. They have a panache to show off. Rohini natives are happy and satisfied and generally do not hold grudges in life.</p>\r\n<p>Education &amp; Profession: Decent Education is suggested. Rohini natives can be successful in both business and jobs. Career related to arts, fashion, sweet and juicy foods as well as materials and cosmetics is favorable. Agriculture especially growth of juicy fruits and vegetables can yield a good income. Extra caution is advised when going for business partnership for Rohini natives. Due to their emotional, kind and simple nature there is a high probability that Rohini natives can be manipulated in business partnership. Generally natives are honest, sincere and truthful at their workplace.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Family Life: Natives are more attached to mothers and mothers relatives. Males and Females have good life partners and children. Natives are happy and satisfied due to kind and caring nature as well as the penchant for not holding any grudges. Natives are loved and honoured by their society due to being honest, sincere and gentle. Though sometimes stubborn and emotional nature causes problems for Rohini natives. Females are advised to avoid suspicion of their partners.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Health: Males natives can have harmonal imbalances due to mental stress. Diseases connected to blood and water are a possibility. Females are likely to suffer from irregular menses and pain in breasts.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Remedies: Praying to Lord Brahma or Lord Shiva is quite beneficial. Since Lord Krishna was born in this nakshtra and nakshatra is in a rashi of shukra holding fasts on friday and praying to lord krishna could also provide beneficial results.&nbsp;</p>', '', 1, 13, '2014-02-02 02:14:21', 899, '', '2014-03-06 11:24:16', 899, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-02-02 02:14:21', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 4, 23, 'rohini nakshatra, nakshatras ruled by chandra', 'rohini nakshatra in vedic astrology', 1, 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(38, 154, 'Mrigashira', 'mrigashira', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Mrigashirsha (also called Mrigashira) is the fifth nakshatra among the <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=category&amp;id=12&amp;Itemid=112">27 Nakshatras</a> studied in Vedic Astrology. It is located in the Orion Constellation. Of the 4 Padas, the first 2 Padas are located in <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=23:vrishabha&amp;catid=11:12-signs&amp;Itemid=111">Vrishabha</a> while the remaining 2 Padas are in <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=24:mithuna&amp;catid=11:12-signs&amp;Itemid=111">Mithuna</a>. The symbol for Mrigashirsha is an antelope''s head while the gana is devta and the presiding deity is <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=2:chandra&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Chandra</a>. Mrigashirsha is rule by <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=3:mangal&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Mangal</a>.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Physical Attributes: Mrigashira natives born in Vrishabha are slightly fairer as compared to Mrigashira natives born in Mithuna. They are physically delicate and quite nervous and restless. They possess a stout body, tall height and moderate complexion along with thin legs and long arms. Females have the more or less the same physical attributes as males. In addition to them Mrigashira females are sharp with a lean body with a good face and facial expressions.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Character/Events: Natives are happy-go-lucky with a good sense of humour and quick wit. They enjoy communication both verbal and written. They are spontaneous, enthusiastic and love socializing. They are quite suspicious and can sense danger. Generally they love lothing and accessories. They have good grasping abilities and can can learn and adapt very quickly. They have a creative nature but take time when they are placed in difficult situation. Mrigashira females like to control their hushand. They are sincere in their dealings and expect the same from others. Blind trust on others leads to frustration, repentance and feeling of being cheated. They turn quite impatient when confontrated with prejudice. Generally life upto 32 years sees problems in settling down. Mrigashira natives born is vrishabha tend to float career paths before finally settling down. Mrigashira natives born in Mithuna can make a good career in accountancy. Besides that poetry, astrology, engineering, teaching and administration are suggested. Mrigashira females are alert, quick-witted but have a poisonous tongue. She is educated and fond of arts. Period upto 32 years is generally slow for career while the period from 33 to 50 years sees maximum career growth and satisfaction. Extra precaution is required to see money is not wasted in later years of life.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Family Life- Despite of having innocent intentions and noble heart, Mrigashira natives rarely enjoy good sibling relationship. Spouse doesn''t keep a good health. There are problems in marital life due to suspicion and quirky humour aimed at spouse. Females are dominant over husbands. Females are very likely to have one or two affairs prior to marriage.</p>\r\n<p>Positives: Sharp intelligence, strong individuality, witty, enthusiastic, quick learner, youthful and sensual.</p>\r\n<p>Negatives: Flirty, impulsvie, fickle minded, need constant attention and sensitive to criticism.</p>\r\n<p>Health: Mrigashira natives suffer from acidity, constipation and shoulder problems in general. Females may also suffer from goiter, pimples, venereal diseases and menstrual troubles.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Remedies: Mrigashira Natives are advised to pray to Chandra and Goddess Parvati.</p>', '', 1, 13, '2014-02-02 02:15:03', 899, '', '2014-03-06 11:27:33', 899, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-02-02 02:15:03', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 4, 22, 'mrigashira nakshatra, nakshatras ruled by mangal', 'mrigashira in vedic astrology', 1, 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(39, 156, 'Ardra', 'ardra', '<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Ardra is the sixth naksthatra among the <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=category&amp;id=12&amp;Itemid=112">27 nakshatras</a>. All the 4 Padas are located in Mithuna. The ruling planet is Rahu while the symbol for Ardra is a human head. The presiding diety is Rudra. Gana of Ardra is Manushya. Since Rahu rules Ardra and location is in Mithuna which is the house of <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=4:buddh&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Budh</a> &amp; <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=8:rahu&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Rahu</a> (according to certain text) the natives have been shown to have characteristics of both Rahu &amp; Budh.</p>\r\n<p>Physical Attributes: Large face, curly hair and sullen expressions have been observed. Though any fixed physical trait is difficult to associate with Ardra natives owing to the mysterious nature of Rahu.</p>\r\n<p>Character/Events: Ardra natives are determined in their responsibilities and get the job done by any means necessary. Moral and Values often take a back seater and success by hook or crook gains precedence. Career in politics is ideal for Ardra natives. There is high probability that native is in politics or politically well connected. Due to Rahu being a karaka for foreign lands, Ardra natives have also been seen to settle abroad and earn their living on foreign lands. Ardra natives are active thinkers and can change personality as the situation demands. Many times they become arrogant, impolite and sarcastic. But mostly they are caring and concerned for others well-being. Due to Ardra location in rashi of Budh there are times when Ardra natives tend to talk a lot on a wide range of topics. Special care is required not to spill out secrets.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; They have special attraction for opposite sex and crave for materialistic lifestyle. Career in profession related to mysteries or solving mysteries like detective, occult subjects, hypnotism, psychology and other less known subjects are ideal. Ardra females in addition to the above mentioned traits are also extravagant in their lifestyle. Female natives can attain good knowledge in a wide range of fields. Period between 32 to 42 years is golden period for ardra natives both male and female.</p>\r\n<p>Family Life: Marriage can be delayed for both the male and female natives. If married early marital fights are possible. Divorce is also possible if marriage takes early. Children can also prove to be source of unease and unhappiness.</p>\r\n<p>Health: Mysterious diseases whose cure is not readily available are possible for Ardra natives. Paralysis, Heart troubles, shoulder problems, asthma are observed in ardra natives. Kidney troubles and diseases of the urinal system are also possible for both males and females.</p>\r\n<p>Positives: Curious mind, hunger for success and knowledge, quick in action, good communication skills and vocational skills. Compassionate for suffering</p>\r\n<p>Negatives: Arrogant, abuses power, mischievous, excessive indulgence, ungrateful and prone to use illegal or anti-social means to achieve success</p>\r\n<p>Remedies: Praying to lord shiva is advised who is always content and calm.</p>', '', 1, 13, '2014-02-02 02:16:30', 899, '', '2014-03-06 11:28:25', 899, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-02-02 02:16:30', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 4, 21, 'ardra nakshatra, 27 nakshatras, nakshatras ruled by rahu', 'ardra nakshatra in vedic astrology', 1, 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(40, 158, 'Punarvasu', 'punarvasu', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Punarvas is the 7th nakshatra among the <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=category&amp;id=12&amp;Itemid=112">27 nakshatras</a>. The benevolent <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=5:guru&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Guru</a> is the ruling planet, presiding diety is Aditi who is known as earth goddess and according to Vedic text was the mother of all devtas. Lord Ram was born in this nakshatra in <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=25:karka&amp;catid=11:12-signs&amp;Itemid=111">Karka</a> rashi. Of the 4 Padas the first 3 Padas are in <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=24:mithuna&amp;catid=11:12-signs&amp;Itemid=111">Mithuna</a> while the remaining last pada is in Karka. Word ''Punarvasu'' is derived from words ''Punar'' and ''Vasu'' which means ''Again'' and ''Live'' respectively. In broad terms Punarvasu signifies to Rise Again, to be Reborn.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Physical Features: Native have good height and oval face. Punarvasu natives tend to be obese in later years of life. Male natives are handsome with long thighs. Some sort of identification mark is present on face or back of the head. Females have curly hair, prominent nonse and sweet speech.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Character/Events: Punarvasu natives are well content in life due to benevolent Guru being the lord of this nakshatra. They generally refrain from illegal/criminal activities to attain their objective. They are simple and straight forward. They have complete faith in god and inclined to follow their religion. They are eager to serve the needy and do not like to cause trouble for others. Generally they have a good education. Owing to their simple nature and content in life they are only moderately successful but rarely suffer from poverty. Females are successful in everything they do. Business partnership is ill-advised for Punarvasu natives. Though wealth maybe moderate, public reputation and dignity is high. Period upto 32 years is difficult. They have special ability to rise up from calamities and no sort of calamity can keep them down for long. They can have successful career in acting, teaching, drama, politics, writing, publishing, philosophical work, working as a scientist and psychologist.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Family Life: Punarvasu natives are the most obedient among the siblings. They have great respect for their parents and elders. They have a good circle of friends. For males a good partner is indicated though the partner may be prone to sickness. Friction in marriage or with family members is indicated for male natives. For females the partner is caring and doting and children are loving. Female natives generally enjoy good family life. House remains orderly.</p>\r\n<p>Health: No major health concern is indicated apart from gastric problems for Punarvasu natives.</p>\r\n<p>Positives: Caring, loving, nurturing, simple lifestyle, satisfaction in life, friendly and religious</p>\r\n<p>Negatives: Unstable in relationship especially males, lack of foresight in business owing to simple nature.</p>\r\n<p>Remedies: Punarvasu natives should pray to Goddess Laxmi.&nbsp;</p>', '', 1, 13, '2014-02-02 02:17:15', 899, '', '2014-03-06 11:29:24', 899, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-02-02 02:17:15', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 5, 19, 'punarvasu nakshatra, 27 nakshatras, nakshatra ruled by guru', 'punarvasu nakshatra in vedic astrology', 1, 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(41, 160, 'Pushya', 'pushya', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Pushya nakshatra is the eight nakshatra among the <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=category&amp;id=12&amp;Itemid=112">27 nakshatras</a>&nbsp;in Vedic Astrology. The word ''Pushya'' means nourishment and accordingly this nakshatra replenishes, nourishes and reinvigorates. Pushya is regarded as the best among the 27 nakshatras. All the auspicious undertakings or purchase of jewelry are done when <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=2:chandra&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Chandra</a> enters Pushya Nakshatra. Pushya is ruled by <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=7:shani&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">shani</a> and its symbol is cow''s udder. The gana is devta and the presiding deity is Brihaspati or <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=5:guru&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Guru</a>. All the 4 Padas of Pushya are in <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=25:karka&amp;catid=11:12-signs&amp;Itemid=111">Karka</a> rashi.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Physical Features: Pushya natives are difficult to discern based on physical characteristics. Since the nakshatra is ruled by Shani, situated in Karka which is Chandra''s rashi and presiding diety is Guru a lot of anomalies are seen in physical traits. Sometimes males are observed to be tall and thin while woman are noticed to be short with an oval face.</p>\r\n<p>Character/Events: Pushya natives are hard working and dedicated to their work. They have a helping nature. The nakshatra of Shani brings control and organization in life of natives through difficult circumstances in early childhood. Poverty is possible upto 15 or 16 years of life. Generally hardships and dependency in early life moulds pushya natives character and they become independent, organized, hard working, sincere and honest individuals. They can work with patience and calm towards achievement of a goal. Careful consideration is required to not overtake a business or project without careful thinking otherwise the desired result may not be ideal. As the natives learn more through experience it is not necessary for them to opt for a difficult course. Hard work and dedication often makes them over burdened at work place. Extra care is required not to overdo things and concentrate on doing the task allocated without getting into the nitty gritty details. As long as skills and abilities are assessed before proceding to work, nothing shall be impossible for the natives. Another impeccable quality is their honesty which does not let them take criminal or illegal tasks. Females apart from qualities mentioned above have peaceful and submissive nature. Pushya natives both males and females cannot properly handle negative criticism or positive feedback.</p>\r\n<p>Family life- Pushya natives are quite attached to their parents. They become independent when they grow up. Spouse for pushya males natives should be self sufficient and with a conservative thinking, dress sense. Females are submissive and cannot express themselves freely. This leads partners to doubt them. Females are devoted and amicable by nature. Both male and female natives have a problem with expressing themselves due to Shani (restrictions) ruling the rashi of Chandra which controls emotions they have difficulties in family life. Many a times natives have to live away from family.</p>\r\n<p>Positives: Hard working, help others, good advisers, honest, dedicated and liked by others.</p>\r\n<p>Negatives: Insecure, Problems in expressing themselves, dogmatic, over sensitive</p>\r\n<p>Health: Shani is dry and cold while Chandra rules all the bodily fluids. Thereby problems related to body fluids like hormonal problems, cough, cold, asthma or other problems related to Kapha Dosha are possible.</p>\r\n<p>Remedies: Praying to Lord Vishnu is advised for pushya natives.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '', 1, 13, '2014-02-02 02:22:16', 899, '', '2014-03-06 11:30:24', 899, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-02-02 02:22:16', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 4, 20, 'nakshatra ruled by shani, pushya nakshatra, 27 nakshatras', 'pushya nakshatra in vedic astrology', 1, 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(42, 162, 'Ashlesha', 'ashlesha', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Ashlesha is the ninth nakshatra among the <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=category&amp;id=12&amp;Itemid=112">27 nakshatra</a> studied in Vedic Astrology. It is ruled by <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=4:buddh&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Budh</a>&nbsp;and all the 4 Padas are located in <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=25:karka&amp;catid=11:12-signs&amp;Itemid=111">Karka</a> rashi. The symbol for Ashlesha is a coiled snake and presiding diety is Naga. According to Valmiki Ramayan the twin brothers Laxman and Shatrughan were born in this nakshatra.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Physical Features: Natives have a pentrating glare which can hyponitize and mesmerize its prey, very much like a snake. Also they have an intriguing speech and a way with words. They have a stout body and brownish complexion. They do not have much resistance power. Looks are not the most attractive either.</p>\r\n<p>Character/Events: Natives have to accept responsibility at a very young age due to parents not alive or abandoning the native. This makes the native very possesive in nature for other relationship as he can''t stand the sight to lose them. Inspite of emotional insecurities the natives can be quite self-centred. They make quite good politicians with their mezmerizing body language and attractive speeches. Ofcourse Ashlesha natives are more associated with cunning, deceit and corrupt so you rarely see honest administrators in this nakshatra. They are often deceitful and can be quite cruel sometimes. Native is emotionally insecure and seldom suffer from mental diseases like schizophrenia and paranoia. Too much of suspicion in life invites all sorts of mental worries. While they are open to criticizing others they do not welcome personal criticism. Career in Politics, as a Physician, Psychologist, Applied Medicines, Chemical Engineer, Chemist and in Sex Rackets is possible.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Family Life: Often abandoned by parents at early age when Ashlesha nakshatra is in lagna. Chandra in ashlesha makes a native insecure and sometimes leads to suspicion and worries. Natives over possessive nature becomes a problem in relationship. Chandra in ashlesha makes a native insecure and sometimes leads to suspicion and worries. Native is not able to give the space needed for a relationship to thrive Too much criticism and poisonous tongue can also damage relationship. Unable to co-exist in surrounding environment.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Positives: Intelligent, Learned, Mesmerizing, Leadership Qualities.</p>\r\n<p>Negatives: Mental Instability, Deceitful, Possessive, Secretive and Talkative.</p>\r\n<p>Health: Mental disease are possible for Ashlesha natives. Also flatulence and stomach problems possible.</p>\r\n<p>Remedies: For the suspicious nature, poisonous tongue and mental insecurities praying to Lord Shiva is best. To calm the talkative and manipulative nature prayers to Lord Ram or Lord Vishnu are advised.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '', 1, 13, '2014-02-02 02:23:50', 899, '', '2014-03-06 11:42:15', 899, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-02-02 02:23:50', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 4, 18, 'ashlesha nakshatra, 27 nakshatras, nakshatras ruled by mercury, nakshatras ruled by buddh', 'ashlesha nakshatra in vedic astrology', 1, 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(43, 164, 'Magha', 'magha', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Magha is the tenth nakshatra among the <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=category&amp;id=12&amp;Itemid=112">27 Nakshatras</a> studied in Vedic Astrology. All the 4 Padas of Magha are situated in the rashi of <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=26:simha&amp;catid=11:12-signs&amp;Itemid=111">Simha</a> (ruled by Surya) and Magha is ruled by Ketu. In accordance with it Magha natives have qualities of both Surya and Ketu endowed. Magha''s symbol is a royal throne which symbolizes power, status and prestige. Magha''s gana is Daitya/Rakshasha while its presiding diety are the forefathers. Surya''s placement in Magha between 1 and 10 ( = degree) indicates it is in its Mool Trikona position. This placement makes Surya feel like an emperor which can grant gifts and benediction. Magha comes under the category of Ganda Moola Nakshatra.</p>\r\n<p>Character/Events: Magha natives are endowed with qualities of both <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=1:surya&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Surya</a> and <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=9:ketu&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Ketu</a>. Magha natives are powerful, influential and short tempered. But at the same time they are spiritual and quite generous. Magha natives are optimistic and free spirited. Magha natives obtain fame which can last through generations. Magha females have a frank and courageous nature. At the same time they are charming and have an interesting personality. These qualities invite many fr-enemies. Female natives love their family and can go to any lengths to safeguard their families interest. Such actions can be used by fr-enemies against Magha Females.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Males have a proud and arrogant nature and command respect from their peers. Public status and financial dignity are generally secure for magha natives. Magha natives respect their elders and are god fearing. They are generous and donate money for noble causes and philanthropic activities. Although Magha natives achieve quite good status and wealth they are better off not to pursue an individual business. Their straight forward nature and generous character can lead to loss making in business. This applies for both male and female natives born with <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=2:chandra&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Chandra</a> in Magha. Magha natives are the ideal middle man or coordinators in work place. Career in top management position is a good option. Also career in politics, law and career as coordinators and brokers is viable.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Family Life: Magha males have good and faithful wife. Females are religious minded and devoted to their husbands. Inspite of that their simple and straight forward nature invites frictions in marriage and family life. Even in the modern day world there are places where woman raising her voice and giving a frank opinion is not invited. Normally both male and female natives have very few friends.</p>\r\n<p>Health: Magha natives may suffer from burns, boils and piles. Night blindness and eye problems are also a possibility.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Positives: Intelligent, Dependable and Smooth Coordinators</p>\r\n<p>Negatives: Arrogant, Hot Tempered, Susceptible to Criticism and Flattery.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Remedies: Performing religious yagnas and Shradha for obtaining blessings of forefathers.&nbsp;</p>', '', 1, 13, '2014-02-02 02:24:19', 899, '', '2014-03-06 11:43:02', 899, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-02-02 02:24:19', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 3, 17, 'magha nakshatra, 27 nakshatra, ganda moola nakshatra, nakshatra ruled by ketu', 'magha nakshatra in vedic astrology', 1, 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(44, 166, 'Purva Phalguni', 'purva-phalguni', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Purva Phalguni is the eleventh nakshatra among the <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=category&amp;id=12&amp;Itemid=112">27 Nakshatras</a> in Vedic Astrology. All the 4 Padas of Purva Phalguni are in <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=26:simha&amp;catid=11:12-signs&amp;Itemid=111">Simha</a> rashi and the ruling planet is Shukra. Gana is Manushya/Human and the Presiding diety is <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bhaga" target="_blank">Bhaga</a> who is one of the <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/%C4%80dityas" target="_blank">12 Adityas</a>. Symbol for Purva Phalguni is a swinging hammock (Jhula).</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;This nakshatra is called Bhagadaivata Star. All the good things in life like pleasure, prosperity, love, enjoyment and sensual blessings are possible through blessings of this nakshatra. A nakshatra ruled by <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=6:shukra&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Shukra</a> in the rashi of <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=1:surya&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Surya</a> is precipice for good fortune, luck and prosperity.&nbsp;<span style="color: #333333; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;"><span><br /></span></span><span>&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>Physical Features: Purva Phalguni females have an oval face and well built figure. They are soft and cultured but prone to arrogance. Males have a healthy constitution, attractive personality and mixed color. Purva Phalguni Natives both males and females are energetic and restless.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Character/Events: Natives have a strong desire to be liked and noticed by others. They are fond of music and arts. They generally avoid conflicts and disputes and try to solve conflicts peacefully through tact. Natives like to travel to places where weather is clear and bright like sunny beaches or mountains. Natives enjoy freedom and do not like working under subordination. If employed at a workplace, the tend to change their jobs frequently until 45 years of age. Period after 45 years of age sees power and authority. They generally oppose to getting benefits at the cost of others. Natives like to be clean and tidy. Purva Phalguni natives are better off with starting their own business venture or earning an independent livelihood through arts or music. It is difficult for natives to learn new things as their scope is limited to earning fame and fortune. Career as Actors, Models, Musicians, Retail Sales, Travel Agents, Cosmetics, Jewelry, Wedding Planners, Sex Therapist and Marriage Counselor is possible.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Family Life: Both male and female natives enjoy happiness and enjoyment in married life. Both the life partner and children provide happiness to individuals. Love marriage is more likely compared to arranged marriage. Native resides away from birth place and family members. Purva Phalguni natives have a good circle of friends and are quite popular in their group. Extra-marital affairs is a possible scenario for Purva Phalguni natives.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Positives: Creative, Intelligent, Charming, Carefree, Open Minded, Refined, Youthful</p>\r\n<p>Negatives: Indulgent, Impulsive, Promiscuous Nature, Narcissism.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Health: Dental problems are possible.</p>\r\n<p>Remedies: Prayers to Goddess Laxmi. Seva and Pooja of Shiva Linga is also beneficial.&nbsp;</p>', '', 1, 13, '2014-02-02 02:25:41', 899, '', '2014-03-06 11:49:26', 899, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-02-02 02:25:41', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 6, 16, 'purvaphalguni nakshatra, purva phalguni nakshatra, nakshatra ruled by shukra, nakshatra ruled by venus', 'purva phalguni nakshatra in vedic astrology', 1, 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(45, 168, 'Uttara Phalguni', 'uttara-phalguni', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Uttara Phalguni is the twelfth nakshatra among the <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=category&amp;id=12&amp;Itemid=112">27 Nakshatras</a> studied in Vedic Astrology. The gana for Uttara Phalguni is Manushya/Human while the ruling planet is <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=1:surya&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Surya</a>. Presiding diety is <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Aryaman" target="_blank">Aryaman</a> and the symbol is a bed. The 1st Pada of this nakshatra is located in <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=26:simha&amp;catid=11:12-signs&amp;Itemid=111">Simha</a> rashi while the remaining 3 Padas are located in <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=27:kanya&amp;catid=11:12-signs&amp;Itemid=111">Kanya</a> rashi. In accordance the natives with <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=2:chandra&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Chandra</a> in 1st Pada show characteristics of Surya like arrogance, leadership skills and intolerant nature while the natives with Chandra in the remaining 3 Padas show characteristics of <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=4:buddh&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Budh</a> like chatty and articulate nature.</p>\r\n<p>Physical Features; Natives of Uttara Phalguni have some sort of prominent mark like black mole on neck or face. Male natives are tall and chubby with large face and long nose. Women born in Uttara Phalguni have a soft voice. Natives born in 1st Pada of Uttara Phalguni have good health and eyesight as well as attractive eyes.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Character/Events: Uttara Phalguni natives are born social workers. They are quite helpful to their friends, family and generally to all in need. While natives of the 1st Pada maybe arrogant and proud due to the combination of Surya Nakshatra (Uttara Phalguni ) + Surya rashi (<a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=26:simha&amp;catid=11:12-signs&amp;Itemid=111">Simha</a>), the natives born in other 3 Padas are simple and straight forward. While natives of 1st Pada maybe irritating they do get high position in life. It has been observed that females can make quite a good career as actress if they are born when 1st Pada of Uttara Phalguni is in lagna/ascendent. Natives of 1st Pada are hot tempered while the natives of other 3 Padas which fall in Kanya rashi resolve conflicts through discussion. Uttara Phalguni natives often see meaningful progress after 38 years of life have passed. Uttara Phalguni natives can have wonderful career as Social Worker, Philantrophist, Actors, Mathematician, Astrologers and Astronomers.</p>\r\n<p>Family Life: Generally for male natives in Uttara Phalguni married life possesses little or no friction. Women can get a good partner and children. Women are good in managing matters of domestic life.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Positives: Ambitious, Good Communicator, Generous</p>\r\n<p>Negatives: Ego, Stubborn and Over-giving</p>\r\n<p>Health: Health remains good with no major complications unless some bad placement in horoscope is present.</p>\r\n<p>Remedies: Praying to Surya and chanting of the Gayatri Mantra.&nbsp;</p>', '', 1, 13, '2014-02-02 02:26:26', 899, '', '2014-03-06 11:51:43', 899, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-02-02 02:26:26', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 3, 15, 'uttaraphalguni nakshatra, uttara phalguni nakshatra, nakshatra ruled by surya, nakshatra ruled by sun', 'uttara phalguni nakshatra in vedic astrology', 1, 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(46, 170, 'Hasta', 'hasta', '<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Hasta is the the thirteenth nakshatra among the <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=category&amp;id=12&amp;Itemid=112">27 nakshatras</a> studied in Vedic Astrology. All the 4 Padas are located in <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=27:kanya&amp;catid=11:12-signs&amp;Itemid=111">Kanya</a> rashi. The gana is devta and the presiding diety is <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Savitr" target="_blank">Savitr</a> who is one of the 12 Adityas. Hasta Nakshatra is ruled by <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=2:chandra&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Chandra</a> and located in the rashi of <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=4:buddh&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Budh</a>. This awkward Budh-Chandra relationship can sometimes cause nervous disorders as Budh (rules the nervous system) and Chandra (rules the mind and thoughts) are planetary enemies.</p>\r\n<p>Physical Appearance: Female natives can be chubby with a fat stomach and prominent chest region. Males though typically less attractive make up with an attractive personality. Both male and female natives could be tall with scar on upper right hand or below shoulders.</p>\r\n<p>Character/Events: Hasta females have a warm but lazy character. Hasta females only work when required but handle task cheerfully and with energy. Female natives are generally cheerful and do not stay angry for long. Hasta males are clever, witty and entertaining. They like to keep company of females. Hasta natives of both gender are a great company to have. Natives are unable to adapt to new technology and thoughts and prefer the old traditions and customs. Hasta natives get respect and honor from public. There is a possibility for fluctuations in life through mental, physical and social factors.&nbsp; Moderate success is observed for natives with&nbsp; help coming from unexpected quarters. Natives are better to pursue a career in business and can make good advisers. A good all round knowledge is observed in the natives and capability to solve disputes peacefully is a trait among natives. Period from 30 to 42 years is golden period of life. Career as craftsmen, Artist, Writers, Painters, Teachers, Adviser, Volunteer Work. Hospital Staff, Counselors, Astrologer, Travel Industry and Comedians is possible.</p>\r\n<p>Family Life: Hasta natives have a tendency to give parental guidance especially in a relationship. They do not see their partner as their equal but rather someone who needs parenting. Marriage for Hasta Natives is more satisfying in later years. Partner is simple and capable. No major problems are indicated in married life unless there are other bad planetary combinations or aspect.</p>\r\n<p>Health: Natives may suffer from bad health especially cough and cold. Females may also suffer from rheumatism and piles.</p>\r\n<p>Positives: Creative, Humorous, Practical and Pleasant Personality</p>\r\n<p>Negatives: Emotional instability and Bad Health</p>\r\n<p>Remedies: Hasta natives should pray to Surya.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '', 1, 13, '2014-02-02 02:26:57', 899, '', '2014-03-06 11:52:57', 899, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-02-02 02:26:57', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 3, 14, 'hasta nakshatra, 27 nakshatras, nakshatra ruled by chandra', 'hasta nakshatra in vedic astrology', 1, 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', '');
