(14, 'com_content.article', 'Chandra', 'chandra', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Moon popularly known as Chandra in Vedic Astrology is the planet of affections and emotions. It is a karaka for mind and everything related to it. Moon also affects the blood circulation as well as water portions on the body and on earth. Well that implies nearly 70% of body and of earth are affected by Chandra. Chandra maybe a small planet and it only stays in a rashi for 2.5 days but its implications are huge when you take the co-tenants, rashi and house lords into consideration. Chandra brings tides and ebbs in an ocean and similarly it brings tides and ebbs in a human mind also. Every positive or negative, good or evil, happy or sad, nice or bad thought that comes to an individual is thanks to chandra and associations and afflictions to chandra.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Moon is the closest planet to the earth. Theoretically it is a satellite. Just like satellites are responsible for good and bad signals in a television; Chandra is responsible for good and bad thoughts in an individual. <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=7:shani&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Shani</a> and <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=8:rahu&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Rahu</a> association with Chandra is a prime factor for people with weak or malefic thought process. Of course the rashi occupied by Chandra also plays an important role in shaping the thought process of an individual. Generally speaking association of Chandra to Shani, Rahu, <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=3:mangal&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Mangal</a>, <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=4:buddh&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Budh</a>, <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=1:surya&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Surya</a> and <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=9:ketu&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Ketu</a> is considered bad. Though bear in mind it is not always the case.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Chandra is highly impressionable graha. It quickly takes in the qualities of its rashi, co-tenants and grahas which aspect it.&nbsp;Lets talk in more detail about Chandra and associations with other planets.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Chandra''s association with Surya is called as Amavasya or No Moon. Many astrologers and jyotishis push the panic button once they hear of this scenario. Various havans, poojas and rings are provided to calm these so called horrible scenario. Well the truth couldn''t be farther off. Well Surya is soul and Chandra is the mind and it wouldn''t be so bad if soul and mind become one considering that soul is considered part of god and mind is the most definiting part in an invidual.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Chandra''s association with Mangal is considered auspicious by many astrologers cause it gives abundant wealth. That is partly true but they forget to mention that this association gives rise to a wounded warrior who is always there to take revenge on others.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Chandra''s association with Budh is probably among the worst. Most mental disorders are caused by this association. Chandra controls the mind while Budh takes care of nervous system. Not to mention this association causes an individual to be a chatter box.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Chandra''s association to Guru is probably the best. In a favourable rashi it causes a powerful yoga called Gaja Kesari yoga. It gives abundant wealth, happiness and prosperity.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Chandra''s association with Shukra is also good. It provides abundant love. Most of the romeo-juliet stories are thanks to Chandra-Shukra association. The fairest and most beautiful looking individuals both male and female are very likely to have assocation of Chandra with Shukra.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Chandra''s association with Shani causes Vish Yoga. The mind is constantly in thinking process and nothing comes out of tireless thinking but sadness and worries. Depression is one of the possible scenarious with Shani-Chandra association. But people who learn to control their emotions and adapt to difficulties and changing scenarios become great individuals but that doesn''t come without a struggle.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Chandra with Rahu is bad in general terms. Rahu is cloudy and smokey and causes disruption to natural though process. Simply speaking this association clouds judgement of an individual.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Chandra''s association with Ketu is bad for some and good for some. Ketu is the planet of detachment. Well for those who want to get closer to the god; this placement provides the right tools of obtaining that goal. For those who are too caught up with materialistic success; consider this placement to quite a bother and probably arrange for some counter measures.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Chandra is very small but its implications on human beings are pretty big. It alone is a gentle, calm and caring graha but depending on rashi lordship or co-tenants it could bring peace or havoc in your life. The greatest enemy or friend of an individual is not anyone but his mind and thoughts. Once you control your own mind; controlling this world is not that difficult.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 1, '', 0, 1, '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 899, '', '2014-02-01 11:44:20', 899, '2014-03-19 07:48:24', '*', '2014-02-01 11:44:20', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 2, 83, '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 17, 5, 8, 'chandra in vedic astrology, chandra in astrology, chandra in 12 bhava, chandra in 12 rashi', 'chandra in vedic astrology', 10, '', 1),
(15, 'com_content.article', 'Mangal', 'mangal', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Mars popularly known as Mangal is another planet along with Shani who invokes fear in the minds of people especially for those who are of the age where marriage takes priority. A Mangal Dosha is a tragedy for the bride/groom and their parents yet a boon for the astrologers. No one is bothered to know that the very word "Mangal" means good and auspicious. Ofcourse mars is a fiery planet and has his sort of problems associated with itself but it is better to understand why this fiery planet is so angry and cold before making any judgement on people who are influenced very highly by this planet.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Mangal is considered a male planet. To be more precise people born under the infuence of mars are the macho types. These includes females also. The ladies who like to order, shout and get angry to get things done are mostly under the influence of a strong mars in horoscope. Mars has a lot of high octane energy. People under the influence of Mars keep on doing relentless work, want everything on time, get angry at smallest inaccuracies of co-workers or employees and worst of all keep others on their toes. Mars hates laziness and lies. These are the reasons why they are the ideal employees but not-so great employers. Mangal is least likely to cause downfall of others. They may get angry, make enemies, use harsh speech but they rarely ever keep enemity for lives. They may get angry very fast but their anger also calms down after some time. But none the less Mangal does have its share of handicaps.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; Mangal is impatient and very harsh in speech. People under influence of Mars often make rash decisions and make enemies out of people due to their high moral values and principles. The world is not so honest and sincere. It is full of scums and leeches who thrive on looting and cheating others. Since Mangal cannot stand these things he is always at logger-heads with these people. A bride or groom who has Mangal in a prominent position cannot compromise on his/her ideals and principles. That is why a lot of quarrels happen and eventually divorces happen. Ofcourse astrologers do not help the cause by matching partners with Mars or <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=7:shani&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Shani</a>&nbsp;in a prominent position of the partner.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; None the less Mars does have its good side. Mars influence people easily sacrifice their own goodwill for people for whom they care. They would give up their profit for others to avoid loss. If any sort of association with Jupiter is present they could even bear loss if those they care for are profited from their sacrifice.&nbsp;Most of the prominent actors, sportsperson, celebrities and good army commanders have Mars in a very good position. Mars influence people do great in places where everything needs to be done on time like railways and armies. They make very competent lawyers and deal makers.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; In my view some people are born for the benefit of the community. They are there to make a difference. Mars influenced people are one of them. They may not be the most charming people to stay around but they are the most trustworthy, hard working and kind hearted people to be friends with.&nbsp;</p>', 1, '', 0, 1, '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 899, '', '2014-02-01 11:45:23', 899, '2014-03-06 07:59:59', '*', '2014-02-01 11:45:23', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 3, 85, '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 0, 3, 7, 'mangal in vedic astrology, mangal in 12 rashi, mangal in 12 bhava, mangal dosha, mangal in astrology, mars in astrology', 'mangal in vedic astrology', 10, '', 1),
(16, 'com_content.article', 'Budh', 'budh', '<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Mercury known as Budh in Vedic Astrology is the prince among planets. Budh is young, talkative and smart. Budh is generally very close to Surya in a horoscope with maximum distance being 28 degrees from each other. Budh provides common sense, speech, communicative skills and also commands the neural processes in the brain. Budh and Guru are almost identical in that both are scholars but in present scenarios the smart and argumentative Budh wins over the knowledgable but dignified Guru. Budh takes the qualities of its co-tenants easily be it good or bad. It is a very impressionable graha. Though Budh doesn''t see most planets as enemies other then Chandra, many see him as their enemy.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; In this age of PR those who can market themselves get more brownie points over others. Thanks to Budh you can effectively communicate your point across to others be it via speech or via writing. Most of the scientific research and innovations are possible due to the ideas and itellact provided by Budh. Be warned that plain old Budh is nothing but sweet talk. It needs a driver to put argument into efforts and theories into practise. Grahas like Mangal, Shani and Surya''s association with Budh are the drivers behind most important inventions. Budh is a businessman or more precisely a sales man. He can sweet talk anybody into buying a product be it good or bad. Most effecient salesman, call centre operatives, shop keepers and marketers need a good Budh for success in their fields. Those who have a weak Budh may suffer from speech defects, bad communicative skills as well as mental disorders.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Budh is a very impressionable graha. Like Chandra it takes the qualities of its rashi, house and co-tenants very easily. A plain old Budh rarely makes or breaks a person. With planet Surya as its co-tenant a very powerful yoga is formed known as Budh-Aditya yoga which provides knowledge, wealth and heppiness. Though not everyone gets the benefit of Budh-Aditya yoga. Association of Budh+Mangal is difficult to judge. Sometimes this association causes catostrophe because Budh is calm while Mangal is restless. Two opposing forces staying in a rashi would provide disaster. But there are times when Budh provides direction to the abundant energy of Mangal. Many great individuals have a favorable association of Budh+Mangal. Many successful lawyers have Budh+Mangal relationship in their horoscope. Budh+Guru is a favorable association by and large. Guru''s knowledge is supported by Budh''s analytical, communicative and argumentative skills. In not so favourable location you could see a thug who uses his knowledge and speech to cheat others. Either way you are guaranteed to see a smart and successful individual when Budh+Guru is there in a horoscope. Budh+Shukra is also a very good combination. Musicians and Artists are likely to have association of Mangal+Budh. Budh+Shani provides good Mathematicians and Chartered Accountants.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Budh is royalty by nature and more importantly royalty without duties. So you can''t expect Budh to understand problems or do proactive work or go out of his way to help others. Budh articulate and refined speech are sure to win over a few people, but long term they are bound to see that he is nothing but trash talk. Budh''s association with Mangal, Shani or Surya in a favorable location provides great results for individual as well as the community.</p>', 1, '', 0, 1, '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 899, '', '2014-02-01 11:46:04', 899, '2014-03-06 08:02:57', '*', '2014-02-01 11:46:04', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 4, 87, '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 0, 3, 6, 'budh in vedic astrology, budh in astrology, budh in 12 bhava, budh in 12 rashi', 'budh in vedic astrology', 10, '', 1),
(17, 'com_content.article', 'Guru', 'guru', '<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; When an astrologer starts to read a horoscope the two things he is going to definitely check for is position of <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=7:shani&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Saturn</a> for bad results and Jupiter for good results. Jupiter is the most benefic planet in a horoscope. Popularly known as guru, it is considered a karaka for wealth, happines and well being. A well placed guru in a horoscope suggests a successful and happy life.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Jupiter is one planet which alone in a good position can liberate from all other negative influence of planets. It gives a positive outlook in life, gives a calm personality and pleasing appearance. A strong guru signifies a person who is learned, smart, calm and dignified. Guru gives a firm and unwavering faith in god and provides knowledge of Truth. Knowledge alone can free a soul from the worldy chains that plague the human soul and takes the soul closer to its maker aka The God.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Jupiter maybe the most benefic planet in a horoscope but it does have its share of negative influence like any other planet. People with Guru in a prominent position often are a bit chubby. Guru promotes well being but unfortunately it promotes laziness and gluttony also. Guru cause a person to be fat, chubby and easy going. When there is a crisis at work they maybe the calmest persons in the office but they will leave the proactive work to people with strong <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=3:mangal&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Mangal</a>. They are the ideal employers and marriage partners but not the most ideal employees. They rarely take up challenges which require them to sweat and they rarely have to drop a sweat to achieve something in life. Connection or Co-tenants like <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=4:buddh&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Budha</a> and <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=6:shukra&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Shukra</a> can cause all hell to break loose. Such people will go to any lenghts to make their pockets bigger and others people''s pockets smaller.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; All said and done, the benefits of Guru far outweigh its drawbacks. People with a strong guru are kind in nature and wonderful friends and family members. They easily get help from all spheres of life. People who crave for an easy lifestyle should definitely hope for a well placed Guru. Those less unfortunate souls who do not have a good disposition of Guru should make their way up the ladder through sheer hard work and dedication</p>', 1, '', 0, 1, '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 1, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 899, '', '2014-02-01 11:46:31', 899, '2014-03-24 07:10:38', '*', '2014-02-01 11:46:31', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 5, 89, '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 1, 5, 5, 'guru in astrology, jupiter in astrology, guru in vedic astrology, guru in 12 bhava, guru in 12 rashi', 'guru in vedic astrology', 10, '', 1),
(18, 'com_content.article', 'Shukra', 'shukra', '<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; When you think of romance and pleasures there is only one planet that can satisfy your quench for them. The name is Venus. Popularly known as Shukra in Vedic Astrology, shukra is the planet of pleasures, luxuries and music. It is identical to <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=5:guru&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Guru</a> as it gives abundant wealth but Shukra also gives pleasures and luxuries. While it does not have the humility to handle fame or wealth, it is guaranteed that a person with prominent Shukra would have lived his/her life to the fullest and given pleasure to all of his/her sensual organs.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Shukra is the kamdeva personified. All the romance in the world is a gift from Shukra. The beautiful women, melodious music and mesmerizing dance moves are all thanks to the great planet called Shukra. The life force or semen which brings another life on this earth is also governed by Shukra. All the sexual organs which provide pleasures are governed by Shukra. The delicacies like Chocolate and Pastries derive their sweetness from Shukra as Shukra is the karaka for Sweetness. The people with a great disposition of Shukra are attractive, wealthy, fashionable and charming. They are admirers of art, music, fashion and beauty.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; While Shukra is a karaka for everything beautiful and gorgeous it does have its downsides. Shukra promotes excessive sweetness and drug addiction. It does not know any limits to pleasures and romance. Most of the taboo activities are carried on when a person is either under the influence of Shukra or with association to Mangal and <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=8:rahu&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Rahu</a>. With <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=3:mangal&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Mangal</a> as a co-tenant or mutual aspect you could find a flirt and even a womaniser. All the marriages done on whims and instant attraction are due to Shukra-Mangal connections. When there is Rahu involved with Shukra marriage may even be with the wrong person and leads to bad reputation for the individual and their close relatives. Shukra causes drug, alcohol and sex addiction. Even addiction to medicines and prescribed drugs is possible with bad placement of Shukra.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Having said that it does do wonderful with <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=2:chandra&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Chandra</a> as co-tenant. The individual with Shukra+Chandra as co-tenant could have a romantic equation of epic proportions on par with Romeo-Juliet or Heer-Ranjhaana and remain inseparable throughout life. Shukra with Guru as co-tenant may give wealth, happiness and knowledge but many a times it is through illegal means. Shukra with Shani is quite bad as Shani''s negativity is a damp squid for sensual and pleasurable Shukra. But since both planets are friendly it rarely causes destruction. An aspect of Shani or Guru on Shukra is quite a blessing to have. Shukra also gives love for animals and provides benefits through them in a favourable placement.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Most beautiful woman and fortunate man have Shukra in a very good disposition. All the famous celebrities have a good Shukra or a favourable period of good Shukra. While Guru may give wealth, happiness and knowledge to a native leave it to Shukra to give you the finer things in life. Shukra natives are like a horse wihout a lease which can run off anywhere he/she pleases. The kind of ecstacy, pleasures and forbidden desires which Shukra provides can only be dreamt by other planets. Fame and fortune is abundant for people with a good Shukra.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Ofcourse with no boundary between acceptance and taboo most of the Shukra influenced people go bonkers after a certain time start resorting to drugs or even medicines to calm their mind. Romance and Sensual pleasures could be over the top but so is the risk of catching a venereal disease. Love takes a backseat and lust would control your mind and body unless there is a limiting aspect of Guru or Shani involved. The price of being a celebrityy is high with no privacy or peace but those who only crave for Page 3 lifestyle should start pleasing dear sweet aunty known as Shukra. For people with problematic Shukra praying to Lord Krishna or Goddess Laxmi for improving the condition and Goddess Santoshi Maa for decreasing the side-effects of afflicted Shukra is highly beneficial.</p>', 1, '', 0, 1, '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 899, '', '2014-02-01 11:46:57', 899, '2014-03-06 08:07:23', '*', '2014-02-01 11:46:57', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 6, 91, '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 4, 3, 4, 'shukra in vedic astrology, shukra in astrology, shukra in 12 bhavas, shukra in 12 rashi, shukra in astrology', 'shukra in vedic astrology', 10, '', 1),
(19, 'com_content.article', 'Shani', 'shani', '<ul class="nav nav-tabs">\r\n<li class="active"><a href="#">Shani</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=79:shani-superstition&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Shani &amp; Superstition</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; The word Shani seems to invoke fear in the hearts of people like no other planet. Shani represents scarcity, fear, oppression, old age and poverty. Well that alone seems to put this humble planet in the category of worst of the worst. By all means Shani can be said to be a malefic planet who brings adversities and havoc in our lives but the perspective has to change regarding how we look at adversities to understand the working of Shani a little more.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Let me start by saying that Shani is appointed as a judge by&nbsp;<a href="http://www.sanatansociety.org/hindu_gods_and_goddesses/shiva.htm">Lord Shiva</a> himself. A normal judiciary functions according to laws of the country and Shani functions according to divine laws of the nature. Shani is aware of most of our karmas and he provides punishments befitting our crimes. Most of the human beings are far from noble souls. We lie, steal, ridicule others and even deceive or backstab others. This is not limited to one birth time but continues over several births and rebirths. Though we may not be aware of these crimes, gramps Shani keeps a watchful eye over these karmas. Remember, he cannot punish you unless you have done some crime. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; So why the fear of gramps Shani? Well, we are human beings after all. We cannot fathom why we need patience, hard work and discipline while the other guy gets the ferraris, the beautiful mansions and the iPhones. The sooner we learn the need for discipline, hard work, patience, fortitude and empathy the sooner does gramps Shani move out of our way. He does give wonderful results to those who plan the long road to success with honest and sincere efforts and plan betterment of the community and world. But those good fruits take a long, long time to come. By that time your patience is tested to the limits and your ego and arrogance is washed away. You are new and renewed all dignified, kind and considerate to your fellow beings. &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; So is gramps Shani good or bad? Well he is bad cause we often plan shortcuts in life and easy way out of misery and suffering. That is the sole reason why Shani makes our lives a miserable hell. Say you are a prisoner in a jail and the warden catches you &nbsp;trying to sneak out of jail before your sentence is over. Most of us would assume that the warden would be very upset and may sentence us to more severe punishment. Same thing applies to Shani but he actually cares for his prisoners and wants them to be contributing members of the society. We do not like Shani cause he is a strict teacher who likes to whip now and then to teach some discipline and hard work to his students. No one likes to learn the things the hard way so to speak.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Having said all this Shani has positive aspects in life also. Most of the guys who grow from rags to riches have Shani in an important disposition in their horoscope. Most of the people who make a difference in lives of others have Shani in exalted or own sign or in a good position. Shani destroys everything that is not sustainable over a long period of time. That includes relationships. Most of the divorces happen during the Saade-Saati or Shani Periods. Though it may seem like hell at that time after some time we come to realise that the relationship couldn''t have worked out and what happened was for the better. Our ego is destroyed and we learn the importance of patience and dignity. At the end of saade-saati most people develop a positive outlook towards lives.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; At the end of the day it all comes down to perspective. A simple, easy-going life is a choice of most but attainable by few. Those who believe in making lemonade, when lemons are provided fare much better in life then those who cry while looking at the lemons. Success is not defined by how high a person rises but how many times a person gets up after falling.&nbsp;</p>', 1, '', 0, 1, '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 899, '', '2014-02-01 11:47:34', 899, '2014-03-06 08:10:11', '*', '2014-02-01 11:47:34', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 7, 93, '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 9, 4, 3, 'shani in vedic astrology, shani in astrology, shani in 12 bhava, shani in 12 rashi, saade-saati, shani and superstition', 'shani in vedic astrology', 10, '', 1),
(20, 'com_content.article', 'Rahu', 'rahu', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Rahu is a shadow planet and is considered the north node of the moon. It is also termed as a dragon''s head in some places while in vedic astrology Rahu has the head of a snake. According to vedic astrology, Rahu is responsible for causing eclipse to Sun and the Moon. Rahu is &nbsp;smokey and mysterious. He represents black arts, magic, taboo activities and foreigners. Rahu is an impersonator who tries to show the qualities he does not have. He is considered a malefic planet and astrologers make quite a fortune out of the so-called bad yogas associated with it. Well, the truth couldn''t be further off.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Rahu is a planet in vedic astrology and like in all planet''s case certain rules and regulations apply. The placement of Rahu at time of birth is fixed according to previous life karmas. Rahu is the most accurate measure to judge the sins of previous life karmas depending on his placement in horoscope along with its drishti. Rahu carries the mandate of putting a human being under illusion. Rahu encourages individuals to take risky and foolish decisions which only bring harm and loss for him. Ofcourse, sometimes it gives quite favorable results for people interested in forbidden desires and&nbsp;taboo activites. Not only that money, power, sex and fame are also abundant in a favorable period of Rahu.&nbsp;Most politicians have a very good Rahu. Rahu is a karaka for foreigners and everything mysterious. Rahu is one of the planets which in a favorable position can suggest a successful chance of going and settling abroad. Rahu in 4th house, 9th house and 12th house suggests if individual will live and stay away from home and in foreign locations.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Rahu magnifies the bad effects and lessens the good effects of planet which is its co-tenant. It is generally favorable if Rahu is alone in a house with no co-tenants and not casting drishti on any planet. Rahu causes eclipse to the Sun and the Moon. In other words the intelligence and rational thinking are hindered due to Rahu. Bad decisions, tough luck and mental problems follow. The individuals who have <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=1:surya&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Surya</a>+Rahu or <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=2:chandra&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Chandra</a>+Rahu in the same house are better off when they consult others for major decisions in their lives. Rahu+<a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=3:mangal&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Mangal</a> is not as bad but cause relationships with siblings to go sour and also promotes anger, restlessness along with frustrations at not getting things done on time. Rahu+<a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=5:guru&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Guru</a> is famously known as Viprachandal Yoga. The simple and wise Guru meets Rahu who is full of deceit and camaflouge. Naturally they don''t get along well. Rahu+Shukra is not as bad and actually gives quite good results. People with Shukra+Rahu are often driven by taboo activites and forbidden desires. The bad results of Rahu+Shukra are blind love followed by divorce. Rahu+<a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=7:shani&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Shani</a> gives rise to Shapit yoga. It occurs after a long time and generally people born in these association have quite a hard life due to past life bad karmas.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Rahu is a strange planet to judge cause it is always trying to be pretentious. It tries to mirror <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=6:shukra&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Shukra</a>&nbsp;but he is an imposter. Though in the present age it is quite good to have Rahu in an influental house. Today the world judges book by its cover and people who are engaged in showboating, impersonating and hypocricy enjoy quite good status. All aspiring politicians must hope and pray for a better Rahu.&nbsp;</p>', 1, '', 0, 1, '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 899, '', '2014-02-01 11:48:00', 899, '2014-03-06 08:14:38', '*', '2014-02-01 11:48:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 8, 95, '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 3, 3, 2, 'rahu in vedic astrology, rahu in astrology, rahu in 12 bhavas, rahu in 12 rashi', 'rahu in vedic astrology', 10, '', 1),
(21, 'com_content.article', 'Ketu', 'ketu', '<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Ketu is another shadowy planet like <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=8:rahu&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Rahu</a> which features prominently in Indian Astrology. Along with <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=7:shani&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Shani</a>, <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=3:mangal&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Mangal</a> and <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=8:rahu&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Rahu</a> it gets quite a good bashing from amateur astrologers. It is a malefic planet but that does mean it is literally bad. The facts about Ketu are often misinterpreted to suit the worldy desires so much so that it has lost its divine purpose. Ketu is capable of taking an individual closer to moksha. Only <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=5:guru&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Guru</a> is the other planet which can boasts of this great feat. The final purpose of all living beings is to get closer to the Supreme Entity aka God.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; So why the unnecessary prejudice towards Ketu? Well the fact that Ketu has its own agenda which is free from the social norms, rules and regulations makes it quite a villian for the society. The world is not known to welcome people who go against social norms. Most of people with Ketu in lagna or with <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=2:chandra&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Chandra</a> in horoscope are detached from others and live a solitary life. They have a nihilistic, uncaring and unapologetic attitude towards society as a whole. They are meant to break away from the social bonds which bind the individuals to society. Some of them even resort to total reclusiveness from society in the form of Sanyas. Others less fortunate try to live a detached life while remaining in the society constantly at logger-heads with the cultural norms.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Lets talk of the downside of Ketu in a bad placement for a bit. Ketu is the astrological equivalent word of detachment. Divorces, Separation from loved ones and Solitary Life would send quivers down anyone''s spine. As long as you live in this world ones self is bound to have inclinations towards socialisation, recognition, acceptence, affection and attraction. It is only natural to have these feelings. The greatest of the saints and holy souls desired for such comforts and pleasures. Now the person who lived in solitary confinement and emotional reclusiveness cannot just mix with the society like sugar in water. They would always stick out like a sore thumb. Eventually their desires fade away and they become even more reclusive and paranoid of the society. They loose purpose and motivation in their life. But fear not as Krishna said in the Gita:</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">"<em>One who walks on path towards knowledge and engages in auspicious activities does not meet his end.</em>" --Bhagvad Gita Chapter 6 Verse 40</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; The essence here is person with a good Ketu is naturally detached and not interested in materialistic goals and social confirmity. That alone brings them closer to the Supreme Entity which is the final goal of all human beings. For them their own inner voice is final take on everything. As long as you don''t care about society it would be the highest blessing to have Ketu in lagna or with Chandra or have period of Ketu which brings separation from loved ones. For others who are bonded with society there is a solution to pray to Lord Ganesh to lessen the effects of a malefic Ketu.</p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #000000;">&nbsp;</span></p>', 1, '', 0, 1, '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 899, '', '2014-02-01 11:48:24', 899, '2014-03-06 08:26:01', '*', '2014-02-01 11:48:24', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 9, 97, '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 8, 3, 1, 'ketu in vedic astrology, ketu in astrology, ketu in 12 bhavas, ketu in 12 rashi', 'ketu in vedic astrology', 10, '', 1);
