(32, 'com_content.article', '11th house in horoscope', 'labh-bhava', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;11th house is known as Labh Bhava in Vedic Astrology. Also known as House of Gains, 11th house looks after friendship, elder brothers, networks at market place, social progress, oppurtunities for economic growth, gains and profits from market place. The karaka for 11th house is <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=5:guru&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Guru</a>. Labh Bhava determines income for an individual. If the 11th house and lord of 11th house are in good condition then income of an individual remains healthy. The reverse is true if 11th house and its lord are in bad condition. 11th house also manages the quantity and quality of friends.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;There can be no savings as long as there is not a steady flow of income. It wouldn''t be an overstatement to say that atleast savings department of the <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=11:dhana-bhava&amp;catid=10:12-houses&amp;Itemid=110">2nd house</a> is subservient to the income department of the 11th house. In modern world where Money has gained so much prominense it has led to a scenario where the 11th house dictates terms on many matters of other houses particularly 2nd house, <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=14:putra-bhava&amp;catid=10:12-houses&amp;Itemid=110">5th house</a> and <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=16:kalatra-bhava&amp;catid=10:12-houses&amp;Itemid=110">7th house</a>. No Money means No Savings. No Savings means No Marriage. No Marriage means no Social Identity. While this does not necessarily apply to every individual it holds true for many poor souls. Relationship of 11th house with other house lords could signal income through multiple portfolio''s. The better the condition of 11th house and 11th house lord the more beneficial results are obtained in matters of friends, income, social and business connections as well as chances for growth. Reverse is the case when 11th house and its lord are in problematic condition. While affiliation with the hell houses is not the most ideal scenario it may yield favorable results in the lords of hell house and lord of 11th house are friendly planets.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Labh Bhava also determines your friends and social circle. Imagine no friends on facebook or no connection on google plus or no followers on twitter. No real friends at school, work place or in general life. 11th house along with <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=12:sahaja-bhava&amp;catid=10:12-houses&amp;Itemid=110">3rd house</a> has gained prominence in the last few decades. Today 11th house is much more then means of livelihood and income. It controls your social standing through friends and professional standing through network connections. From a business perspective 11th house is the house of networks at market place. Any thriving business needs to be in contact with influential people at the market place. A good condition of 11th house ensures a businessman is always connected with the right people at the right position at the right time.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Most planets give favorable results in the 11th house baring <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=6:shukra&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Shukra</a>. <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=5:guru&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Guru</a> as the karaka for 11th house is the most ideal planet to have in the 11th house. It increases income, friends and social prestige and also improves networks and business connections. <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=4:buddh&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Budh</a> gives highly communicative, well-connected friends and friends who have a good intellect. <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=7:shani&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Shani</a> in 11th house makes a dedicated worker who improves wealth through sincere hard work. Shukra though bad in 11th house can provide income through arts, fashion and music. <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=8:rahu&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Rahu</a> gives material yearnings and increases association with a wide variety of people.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;11th house is the house which makes or breaks an individual through financial and social means. While it doesn''t have much bearing on the individual as a whole for those who put too much emphasis on money and power it is essential that they have a good 11th house.&nbsp;</p>', 1, '', 0, 1, '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 899, '', '2014-02-01 12:21:25', 899, '2014-03-06 09:41:32', '*', '2014-02-01 12:21:25', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 20, 119, '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 0, 3, 1, 'labh bhava, labh sthana, 11th house, vedic astrology', 'guru in vedic astrology', 11, '', 1),
(33, 'com_content.article', '12th house in horoscope', 'vyaya-bhava', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;12th house is popularly known as Vyaya Bhava in Vedic Astrology. It is the house which gives grief, despair and losses to an individual. Losses are not just monetary but also emotional and physical. As one of the hell houses it can literally put individuals through the motions and create depression and anxities of unparallel quantities. 12th house also rules over prisons, ashrams, hospitals and mental institutions. On a better note it also rules research and doctarate programmes. But the most important of all is that the 12th house provides Moksha to an individual.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;No one likes matters of the 12th house. Who would want to voluntarily go to prisons, hospitals or mental institutions? Who would like depression grief, despair and losses? Impact of 12th house is huge and the tag of Valley of Despair is apt for matters of this house. But after careful observation and practical experience a hypothesis starts to develop that the 12th house is perhaps the most misunderstood house in astrology.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;While not many people reading this article would care to get Moksha, it is essential to know that no rebirth equates to no suffering. For those who do not believe in the concept of Moksha, there is higher knowledge and deeper meaning of life associated with the 12th house. An individual gains an understanding of concepts which are outside the scope of what is already known. This is the reason why research and doctarate programmes are under the wings of the 12th house as these are fields where knowledge is not yet present in this world. For those who don''t care two hoots about Moksha or Knowldge there is the most important aspect called bed pleasures ruled by 12th house. Many marriages break on complaints of incomplete or no sexual satisfaction derived from partners. 12th house ascertains whether you have a good life in bed or not. Perhaps more importantly it guarantees that your marriage is not broken on account of non-existent physical relationship with your partner.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;12th house on the positive side also rules dreams and imagination. All the successful fictional writers are blessed with distinctive and vivid imagination by blessings of the 12th house. Not only that lecturers and researchers, Ashrams and Hospitals run by blessings of the 12th house. 12th house has lots of negatives but equal amount of positives. It all comes down to perspective in the end.&nbsp;</p>', 1, '', 0, 1, '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 899, '', '2014-02-01 12:22:38', 899, '2014-03-06 09:44:36', '*', '2014-02-01 12:22:38', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 21, 121, '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 3, 4, 0, '12th house, vyaya bhava, vedic astrology', '12th house in vedic astrology', 11, '', 1),
(35, 'com_content.article', 'Vrishabha', 'taurus', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Taurus is known as Vrishabha Rashi in Vedic Astrology. It is an earthy sign. By gender it is a female and rules the south direction. It controls the mouth, neck and voice box. It gives both Vata and Kapha Dosha. <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=6:shukra&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Shukra</a> is the lord of Vrishabha Rashi while <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=2:chandra&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Chandra</a> is exalted in Vrishabha Rashi.&nbsp;</p>', 1, '', 0, 1, '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 899, '', '2014-02-01 12:24:41', 899, '2014-03-06 10:32:42', '*', '2014-02-01 12:24:41', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 23, 125, '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 0, 4, 9, 'vrisabha, vedic astrology, taurus, astrology', 'vrisabha in vedic astrology', 12, '', 1),
(36, 'com_content.article', 'Mithuna', 'gemini', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Gemini is known as Mithuna in Vedic Astrology. This windy sign is male by gender and rules the west direction. It gives Vatta Dosha. It rules the chest, hands and rib cage. <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=4:buddh&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Budh</a> is the lord of Mithuna.</p>', 1, '', 0, 1, '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 899, '', '2014-02-01 12:25:34', 899, '2014-03-06 10:46:05', '*', '2014-02-01 12:25:34', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 24, 127, '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 0, 4, 8, 'mithuna, gemini, vedic astrology', 'mithuna in vedic astrology', 12, '', 1),
(37, 'com_content.article', 'Karka', 'cancer', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Cancer is known as Karka Rashi in Vedic Astrology. It is a watery sign and female by gender. It rules the north direction. It gives Kapah dosha. It controls the chest, lungs and heart. <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=2:chandra&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Chandra</a> is the lord of Karka. <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=5:guru&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Guru</a> is exalted in Karka while <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=3:mangal&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Mangal</a> is debilitated in Karka.&nbsp;</p>', 1, '', 0, 1, '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 899, '', '2014-02-01 12:26:19', 899, '2014-03-06 10:48:10', '*', '2014-02-01 12:26:19', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 25, 129, '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 0, 3, 7, 'karka rashi, cancer sign, vedic astrology', 'karka in vedic astrology', 12, '', 1),
(38, 'com_content.article', 'Simha', 'leo', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Leo is called Simha Rashi in Vedic Astrology. &nbsp;The naturally fiery sign rules the east direction and is a male by gender. It gives Pitta Dosha. It controls the stomach, spinal cord and back. <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=1:surya&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Surya</a> is the lord of Simha Rashi.&nbsp;</p>', 1, '', 0, 1, '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 899, '', '2014-02-01 12:27:43', 899, '2014-03-06 10:54:48', '*', '2014-02-01 12:27:43', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 26, 131, '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 0, 4, 6, 'surya, sun in astrology, surya in vedic astrology, leo in astrology', 'surya in vedic astrology', 12, '', 1),
(39, 'com_content.article', 'Kanya', 'virgo', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Virgo is known as Kanya Rashi in Vedic Astrology. It is an earthy sign, female by gender and rules the south direction. It give both Vata Dosha and Kapha Dosha. <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=4:buddh&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Budh</a> is the lord of Kanya Rashi. Budh is exalted and <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=6:shukra&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Shukra</a> is debilitated in Kanya Rashi.&nbsp;</p>', 1, '', 0, 1, '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 899, '', '2014-02-01 12:30:47', 899, '2014-03-06 10:55:02', '*', '2014-02-01 12:30:47', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 27, 133, '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 0, 4, 5, 'kanya rashi, virgo sign, vedic astrology', 'kanya in vedic astrology', 12, '', 1),
(40, 'com_content.article', 'Tula', 'libra', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; Libra is known as Tula Rashi in Vedic Astrology. The windy sign rules the west direction and is a male by gender. It controls the kidneys and urinary system as well as sexual organs. It gives Vatta Dosha. <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=6:shukra&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Shukra</a> is the lord of Tula Rashi. <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=7:shani&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Shani</a> is exalted and <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=1:surya&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Surya</a> is debilitated in Tula Rashi.&nbsp;</p>', 1, '', 0, 1, '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 899, '', '2014-02-01 12:34:24', 899, '2014-03-06 10:56:13', '*', '2014-02-01 12:34:24', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 28, 135, '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 0, 5, 4, 'tula rashi, libra sign, vedic astrology', 'tula rashi in vedic astrology', 12, '', 1),
(41, 'com_content.article', 'Vrischika', 'scorpio', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Scorpio is known as Vrischika Rashi in Vedic Astrology. This watery sign is a female by gender and rules over the north direction. It controls the uterus, bladder and excretary system. <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=3:mangal&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Mangal</a> is the lord of Vrischika Rashi while <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=2:chandra&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Chandra</a> is debilitated in Vrischika Rashi.&nbsp;</p>', 1, '', 0, 1, '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 899, '', '2014-02-01 12:36:13', 899, '2014-03-06 10:58:09', '*', '2014-02-01 12:36:13', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 29, 137, '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 0, 3, 3, 'vrischika rashi, scorpio sign, vedic astrology', 'vrischika in vedic astrology', 12, '', 1),
(42, 'com_content.article', 'Dhana', 'sagittarius', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Saggitarius is popularly known as Dhana Rashi (not to be confused with <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=11:dhana-bhava&amp;catid=10:12-houses&amp;Itemid=110">dhana bhava</a>) in Vedic Astrology. Dhana Rashi is a fiery sign, by gender a male and rules the east direction. It causes Pitta Dosha. It controls the thighs. <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=5:guru&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Guru</a> is the lord of Dhana Rashi and <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=8:rahu&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Rahu</a> is said to be neecha in Dhana Rashi.&nbsp;</p>', 1, '', 0, 1, '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 899, '', '2014-02-01 12:43:34', 899, '2014-03-06 10:59:53', '*', '2014-02-01 12:43:34', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 30, 139, '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 0, 4, 1, 'dhana rashi, saggitarius sign, vedic astrology', 'dhana rashi in vedic astrology', 12, '', 1),
(43, 'com_content.article', 'Makara', 'capricorn', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Capricorn is popularly known as Makara in Vedic Astrology. This earthy sign is female by gender and rules the south direction. It gives both Vatta and Pitta Dosha. It controls both the knee joints and parts around it. <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=7:shani&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Shani</a> is the lord of Makara Rashi. <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=3:mangal&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Mangal</a> is exalted and <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=5:guru&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Guru</a> is debilitated in makara.</p>', 1, '', 0, 1, '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 899, '', '2014-02-01 12:44:07', 899, '2014-03-06 11:05:31', '*', '2014-02-01 12:44:07', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 31, 141, '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 0, 4, 2, 'makara rashi, capricorn sign, vedic astrology', 'makara rashi in vedic astrology', 12, '', 1),
(44, 'com_content.article', 'Kumbha', 'aquarius', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Aquarius is known as Kumbha in Vedic Astrology. This windy sign has a male gender and rules the west direction . It gives Vayu Dosha. It rules the feet especially the parts below knee joints. <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=7:shani&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Shani</a> is the lord of Kumbha rashi while <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=8:rahu&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Rahu</a> is said to be exalted in Kumbha.&nbsp;</p>', 1, '', 0, 1, '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 899, '', '2014-02-01 12:45:20', 899, '2014-03-06 11:10:21', '*', '2014-02-01 12:45:20', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 32, 143, '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 0, 4, 1, 'kumbha rashi, aquarius sign, vedic astrology', 'kumbha rashi in vedic astrology', 12, '', 1),
(45, 'com_content.article', 'Meena', 'pisces', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Pisces is known as Meena Rashi in Vedic Astrology. It is a watery sign, female by gender and rules the north direction. It gives Kapha Dosha. It rules the foot and heels. <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=5:guru&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Guru</a> is the lord of Meena Rashi. <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=6:shukra&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Shukra</a> is exalted and <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=4:buddh&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Budh</a> is debilitated in Meena Rashi.&nbsp;</p>', 1, '', 0, 1, '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 899, '', '2014-02-01 12:46:18', 899, '2014-03-06 11:12:30', '*', '2014-02-01 12:46:18', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 33, 145, '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 0, 4, 0, 'pisces sign, meena rashi, vedic astrology', 'pisces in vedic astrology', 12, '', 1),
(46, 'com_content.article', 'Ashvini', 'ashvini', '<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Ashvini Nakshatra is the first of the <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=category&amp;id=12&amp;Itemid=112">27 Nakshatras</a> in the Cosmos which are studied in Vedic Astrology. All the 4 Padas of this Nakshatra are located in <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=22:mesha&amp;catid=11:12-signs&amp;Itemid=111">Mesha</a>. Ashvini is ruled by <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=9:ketu&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Ketu</a>. According to ancient vedic literature there are two gods by the name of Ashwini Kumars who are said to be the doctors of the Devtas (Vedic Gods) having vast knowledge of medicines. The name of Ashvini Nakshatra is derived from those gods. Symbol for Ashvini Nakshatra is a horse. Ashvini rules all forms of transport espeially speedy vehicles. Ashvini holds the vast knowledge of medicines and cures for ailments.</p>\r\n<p>Physical Attributes: Males born under this nakshatra have good facial expressions. Eyes are large and bright. Forehead is broad and nose is a little bigger. Females born in this nakshatra have bright but small eyes like a fish. Ashvini Females have alluring looks and magnetic personality.</p>\r\n<p>Character &amp; General Events: Natives of Ashvini are spontaneous and like to get things done in a hurry. Ashvini Natives have an adventurous spirit that is blindely attracted to unknown challenges. They are competent workers who perform above average at the workplace. They are straight forward and prefer a no-nonsense approach in matters of business. Ashvini Natives have generally good health but sometimes suffer from bile complaints.</p>\r\n<p>Education &amp; Profession: Ashvini natives can have great careers as psychologists, therapist, physicians, music, horse trainers, jockeys, transport or as a race car driver. Education which leads to these mentioned careers is better if pursued. Having said that Ashvini Natives can be successful in almost all endeavours they take up and they are fond of literary pursuits. Period up to 30 years generally comes with a lot of struggles. Thereafter period between 30 to 55 years old sees gradual and steady progress being achieved.</p>\r\n<p>Family Life: Due to unrelenting behaviour Ashvini natvies are often subjected to harsh treatment by family especially the father. But inspite of such treatment, an Ashvini Native loves his family implicitly. There is a high chance of having a twin sibling for Ashvini Natives especially in Kumbha Lagna. Marriages for female natives generally takes place between 23 to 26 years while for males marriage takes place between 26 to 30 years of age. Natives are faithful to those who love them.</p>\r\n<p>Positives: Natives of this nakshatra are hard working and diligent. They are not the type to leave a job at half way. They are focused and like to get on with things without fuzz. They are ideal people who can heal a person who is heart broken provided they are in the right frame of mind.</p>\r\n<p>Negatives: They often have an unsteady mind and are quite short tempered. Their desire to extract revenge on their enemies at any cost is quite harmful. They are also fearless and stubborn who don''t think of results when they take on a task.</p>\r\n<p>Remedies: Since Ashvini is rule by Ketu praying to Lord Ganesha is ideal. Also wearing bright colors could help. Career in healing and medicine could make them have kindness and empathy for others.</p>', 1, '', 0, 1, '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 899, '', '2014-02-01 12:49:33', 899, '2014-03-06 11:18:33', '*', '2014-02-01 12:49:33', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 34, 147, '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 0, 4, 26, 'ashvini nakhatra, ashwini nakshatra, ganda moola, ganda-moola', 'ashvini nakshatra in vedic astrology', 13, '', 1),
(47, 'com_content.article', 'Bharani', 'bharani', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Bharani is the second among the <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=category&amp;id=12&amp;Itemid=112">27 Nakshatras</a> studied in Vedic Astrology. It is ruled by <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=6:shukra&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Shukra</a> and all of the 4 Padas are located in <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=22:mesha&amp;catid=11:12-signs&amp;Itemid=111">Mesha</a>. Gana of Bharani is human. Bharani is symbolized by an elephant and represents the female sexual organs. The devta which rules over Bharni is Yama who is also called Dharma.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Physical Attributes: Males born in this nakshatra have large forehead and less hair. Their height is medium-sized and they have beautiful teeth. If the birth is at noon then native could be very tall with a long neck and face. Females of this nakshatra have a good physique and white teeth.</p>\r\n<p>Character &amp; Events: Bharani is ruled by Shukra and located in the rashi of <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=3:mangal&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Mangal</a>. This Mangal+Shukra combo ensures that native is over indulgent and extravagant in his lifestyle. Naturally it doesn''t go down well with those around. With the presiding deity being Dharma (Yama), the bharani native is bound to act on his own sense of justice. This native is unlikely to pursue a work which is wrong according to his conscience. Bharani Native is bound to face a lot of resistance and failures in his life. Bharani native is likely to spoil a good relationship over trivial matters and generally acts on his whims and fancies.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Education &amp; Profession: Education and Career in Food and Beverages as well as hospitality sector is possible. Also other areas like administration, sports, music and occult science can give means of livelihood. Women can achieve a good career in sports industry. Though stability is rarely felt native does see progress in all sectors of life after 33 years of age. Native can be a good cosmetic surgeon or a judge. Cultivation of tobacco could also yield a good income.</p>\r\n<p>Family Life: Bharani natives like to dominate and do not like being dominated especially the female natives. Female natives enjoy love and satisfaction from her husband but is troubled by in-laws. Bharani natives love their family and do not like separation from their families. Male natives are blessed with wise and beautiful life partner. Marriage for females take around 23 years while marriage for males occurs around 27 years of age.</p>\r\n<p>Health: Females could have menstrual problems, uterus disorders, anemia while male natives may suffer from heart problems and lung problems due to smoking. Other possible diseases include fever, body pain and diabetes.</p>\r\n<p>Positives: Bharani natives have an attractive personality and beautiful looks. People are often influenced by their poise and approach. They do not like to pretend . They rarely attract conflict and try to solve conflicts through peaceful means, tact and diplomacy.</p>\r\n<p>Negatives: Natives are fond of partying and over indulgent in luxurious ways. They are quite majestic and behave impulsively.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Remedies: Praying Shiva, Yama or Kali. For females praying any goddess which denotes happiness, family and prosperity is advised.&nbsp;</p>', 1, '', 0, 1, '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 899, '', '2014-02-02 02:08:55', 899, '2014-03-06 11:20:13', '*', '2014-02-02 02:08:55', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 35, 149, '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 0, 4, 25, 'bharani nakshatra, nakshatras ruled by shukra', 'bharani nakshatra in vedic astrology', 13, '', 1),
(48, 'com_content.article', 'Krittika', 'krittika', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Krittika is the 3rd nakshatra among the <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=category&amp;id=12&amp;Itemid=112">27 nakshtras</a> studied in Vedic Astrology. Krittika is ruled by <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=1:surya&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Surya </a>and symbolized by an axe. Among the 4 Padas the 1st Pada of Krittika is in <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=22:mesha&amp;catid=11:12-signs&amp;Itemid=111">Mesha</a> while the remaining 3 Padas are in <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=23:vrishabha&amp;catid=11:12-signs&amp;Itemid=111">Vrishabha</a>. The gana of Krittika is Rakshasha and presiding god is Agni. According to popular texts the 6 stars in Krittika Nakshatra are said to be mothers of Kartikeyan. It is also suggested that Kartikeyan got his name from his six mothers.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Physical Attributes: Males and Females have medium height. They have a thick neck along with a stout and solid body. Males have well-developed muscles.</p>\r\n<p>Character &amp; Events: Natives who belong to the 1st Pada of Krittika Nakshatra show the aggressive qualities of <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=3:mangal&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Mangal</a> while the other 3 Padas show steady and calm attitude of Vrishabha Rashi. Often both males and females are arrogant and freedom loving. They have few friends due to their ego. Krittika natives do not like criticism levelled at them. Female natives are quite quarrelsome. If Surya is in good condition then natives are endowed with enhanced stamina and conviction to pursue goals. Otherwise Krittika natives rarely pursue any hobby or task for long. They do not think of consequences when they start a task. Not pursuing task till the end result in loss and failures.</p>\r\n<p>Education &amp; Profession: Krittika Natives can work in any sector but rarely ever master any sector of work. Natives often work away from hometown. Partnership is not suitable for them due to ego and arrogant nature. Ideal to work in government jobs but business in meat import/export, fashion design, hair stylist and medical especially autopsy is recommended. Both male and female natives can be good administrators if other planets are in favorable location.</p>\r\n<p>Family life: Males often marry a good wife who is devoted and dedicated. Wife is likely an effective administrator at home. Native''s wife may face health issues and sometimes their wife separate from natives due to unforeseen circumstances. Life upto 50 years is full of hardships. For male natives love marriage in indicated and often to a family friend. For females there maybe late marriage or divorce due to arrogant attitude and fierce nature. Ultimately result of separation and secluded life is a possible scenario for female natives of Krittika Nakshatra. Taking care of anger and frustration is advised for Krittika Females.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Health: Female natives may suffer from physical and mental ailments due to excessive work. Tuberculosis, Gastric Problems, Piles, Brain Fever, Boils, Accidents and Wounds are possible for natives of Krittika Nakshatra.</p>\r\n<p>Positives: Natives are self motivated, bright and honor their commitments. They are courageous and ambitious.</p>\r\n<p>Negatives: Natives are often stubborn and have an unstable mind. They are aggressive and arrogant and often pursue unrealistic dreams.</p>\r\n<p>Remedies: Praying to Kartikeya and Surya. Also chanting Gayatri Mantra is advised.&nbsp;</p>', 1, '', 0, 1, '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 899, '', '2014-02-02 02:13:46', 899, '2014-03-06 11:23:01', '*', '2014-02-02 02:13:46', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 36, 151, '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 0, 4, 24, 'krittika nakshatra, vedic astrology', 'krittika in vedic astrology', 13, '', 1),
(49, 'com_content.article', 'Rohini', 'rohini', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Rohini is the fourth nakshatra among the <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=category&amp;id=12&amp;Itemid=112">27 Nakshatras</a> studied in Vedic Astrology. The gana of Rohini is human and all the 4 Padas of Rohini are in <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=23:vrishabha&amp;catid=11:12-signs&amp;Itemid=111">Vrishabha</a>. Rohini is ruled by <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=2:chandra&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Chandra</a> and the presiding deity is Brahma who is the creator of the Universe. Rohini is symbolized by a chariot pulled by two oxen. In Vedic Texts it is mentioned that Rohini was the most favorite wife of Chandra among the 27 nakshatras (all married to Chandra) and Chandra''s impartial love towards Rohini and neglecting of other wives led Daksha Prajapati to curse Chandra.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Physical Attributes: Both males and females natives of Rohini have attractive eyes and graceful appearance. Males have a slender physique and females have a fair complexion. They are loved and honored due to their charming personality.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Character &amp; Events: Rohini is ruled by Chandra and located in Vrishabha which is a rashi ruled by <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=6:shukra&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Shukra</a>. Naturally the Rohini natives are emotional and attracted to finer things in life. They are highly imaginative and lovers or art, music, dance and sculptures. They have a charming and attractive personality yet can be quite stubborn at times. Generally both males and females are very sensitive and extra caution is advised when dealing with them. Rohini natives have a restless mind and keeping focus on a single activity is next to impossible for them. Rohini natives think with their hearts and not with their heads. This is why they can be easily manipulated. Females are well dressed and well behaved but often short tempered and violent when instigated. They have a panache to show off. Rohini natives are happy and satisfied and generally do not hold grudges in life.</p>\r\n<p>Education &amp; Profession: Decent Education is suggested. Rohini natives can be successful in both business and jobs. Career related to arts, fashion, sweet and juicy foods as well as materials and cosmetics is favorable. Agriculture especially growth of juicy fruits and vegetables can yield a good income. Extra caution is advised when going for business partnership for Rohini natives. Due to their emotional, kind and simple nature there is a high probability that Rohini natives can be manipulated in business partnership. Generally natives are honest, sincere and truthful at their workplace.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Family Life: Natives are more attached to mothers and mothers relatives. Males and Females have good life partners and children. Natives are happy and satisfied due to kind and caring nature as well as the penchant for not holding any grudges. Natives are loved and honoured by their society due to being honest, sincere and gentle. Though sometimes stubborn and emotional nature causes problems for Rohini natives. Females are advised to avoid suspicion of their partners.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Health: Males natives can have harmonal imbalances due to mental stress. Diseases connected to blood and water are a possibility. Females are likely to suffer from irregular menses and pain in breasts.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Remedies: Praying to Lord Brahma or Lord Shiva is quite beneficial. Since Lord Krishna was born in this nakshtra and nakshatra is in a rashi of shukra holding fasts on friday and praying to lord krishna could also provide beneficial results.&nbsp;</p>', 1, '', 0, 1, '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_auth