(88, 'com_content.article', 'Malavya Yoga', 'mala', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Malavya Yoga is one of the Panch Mahapurusha Yoga formed when <a title="shukra article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=6:shukra&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Shukra</a> is in exaltion or swakshetra position and located in one of the <a title="Vishnu Sthana Link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=72:kendra-stahanas&amp;catid=41:main-articles">Vishnu Sthanas</a>. In simple terms when Shukra is located in 1st house, 4th house, 7th house or 10th house and also the rashi of Shukra happens to be <a title="Vrishabha Rashi Link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=23:vrishabha&amp;catid=11:12-signs&amp;Itemid=111">Vrishabha Rashi</a>, <a title="Tula Rashi Link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=28:tula&amp;catid=11:12-signs&amp;Itemid=111">Tula Rashi</a> or <a title="Meena Rashi Link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=33:meena&amp;catid=11:12-signs&amp;Itemid=111">Meena Rashi</a> then Malavya Yoga is formed. Shukra is associated with beauty, wealth, fame and romance. In accordance Malavya Yoga natives beget all the pleasures in life.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Malavya Yoga is one yoga where spiritual progress and character of native suffers but inspite of it all, it is a great yoga to have. For people in today''s world are more concerned with worldly pleasures. After all you are guaranteed sufficient wealth, good physique and beauty, abundant fame and blissful romance and marital life along with good children. It wouldn''t be wrong to say 90% of people would want all this in their life. This yoga is not rare as Shukra move every month or so but what is rarity is if Shukra is not afflicted when Malavya Yoga is formed. Generally Shukra, <a title="Surya Article Link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=1:surya&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Surya</a> and <a title="Budh Article Link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=4:buddh&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Budh</a> travel together rarely at distance of 2-3 rashis from each other. Surya diminishes the effect of planets like Budh and Shukra when it comes together with them in a rashi. So only checking Shukra in Vishnu Sthana and Uccha or Swakshetra rashi won''t guarantee Malavya Yoga.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; Malavya Yoga natives have well developed physique, are strong-minded, wealthy and happy with wife and children. They command good set of vehicles. They are self indulgent, intelligent and if Shukra is in Tula then can be fair in giving justice. They are attractive to others and &nbsp;fond of sexual pleasures. They can even be respected by kings of the country if Malavya Yoga is in good condition.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Downside of all Malavya Yoga is no spiritual progress or character development but upsides far outweigh the downsides.&nbsp;</p>', 1, '', 0, 1, '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 899, '', '2014-03-25 12:16:05', 899, '2014-03-25 11:18:33', '*', '2014-03-25 11:17:58', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 81, 268, '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 0, 3, 0, 'malavya yoga, panch mahapurusha yoga, shukra in swakshetra, shukra in uccha rashi, shukra yogas', 'malavya yoga description', 14, '', 1),
(89, 'com_content.article', 'Bhadra Yoga', 'bhadra', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Bhadra Yoga is formed when Budh occupies the <a title="Vishnu Sthana Links" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=72:kendra-stahanas&amp;catid=41:main-articles">Vishnu Sthanas</a> and is located in Uccha Rashi or Swakshetra. In simpler terms it can only happen in 1st house, 4th house, 7th house or 10th house and if Budh is located in Mithuna Rashi or Kanya Rashi. Bhadra Yoga is one of yogas which forms the Panch Mahapurusha Yoga (PMY). Compared to other PMY yogas the effects are slightly less as Budh is an impressionable graha and staying close to <a title="Surya Article Link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=1:surya&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Surya</a> diminishes its effects. If Budh+Surya happens in <a title="Kanya Rashi Link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=27:kanya&amp;catid=11:12-signs&amp;Itemid=111">Kanya Rashi</a> or <a title="Mithuna Rashi Link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=24:mithuna&amp;catid=11:12-signs&amp;Itemid=111">Mithuna Rashi</a> then along with Bhadra Yoga, an additional Budh-Aditya Yoga is formed which promises intelligence, wealth and fame.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Bhadra Yoga natives have well built body and are youthful in looks. Budh is a prince and to some extent these individuals like princely comforts especially if Budh occupies lagna. Budh is the planet which loves to talk articulately and smartely. They are analytical and possess learning of vivid subjects. Though that doesn''t necessarily translate into knowledge. Budh alone in a rashi is quite talkative even though learned it suits better for native to have a planet like <a title="Mangal Article Link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=3:mangal&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Mangal</a> (his enemy), <a title="Shani Article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=7:shani&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Shani</a>, <a title="Guru Article Link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=5:guru&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Guru</a> or Surya with it. They give direction to the articulate and talkative Budh.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Natives born with Bhadra Yoga are strong, have well developed face and chest, youthful in appearance and brave like a lion. They are ambitious and progressive. They get on quite well with relatives and are always eager to help relatives. They are progressive and innovative and capable of breakthrough in scientific fields if other grahas are suitable. Progress comes gradually for the native.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Though Bhadra yoga is quite good yoga it is even better if one of the above mentioned grahas combines with Budh in rashi of Budh. That would give better results as compared to Budh alone in own rashi in Vishnu Sthanas. &nbsp;</p>', 1, '', 0, 1, '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 899, '', '2014-03-25 12:18:52', 899, '2014-03-25 11:20:09', '*', '2014-03-25 11:19:35', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 82, 270, '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 0, 3, 0, 'bhadra yoga, panch mahapurusha yoga, buddh yogas, budh yogas', 'bhadra yoga description', 14, '', 1),
(90, 'com_content.article', 'Parivartana Yoga', 'payo', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Parivartana Yoga (PY) is the unique yoga which occurs when two planets exchange each other''s houses. It is called Exchange of Houses in astrology. Ancient Vedic Astrology doesn''t tell much about such yogas and most astrologers tend not to focus on such yogas. Parivartana Yoga is not a Raja Yoga but kind of symbiosis agreement between two concerned grahas which is mutually beneficiary.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;What has largely been observed is this yoga can occur quite frequently in either the Lagna Chart or Navamsha Chart and due care needs to be given before judging whether such yoga would prove fruitful or not.&nbsp;Some of the rules for fruition/cancellation of Parivartana Yoga are described below.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>1. PY (Parivartana Yoga) &nbsp;can provide beneficial results if it occurs in either Lagna Chart or Navamsha Chart.</p>\r\n<p>2. If two natural benefics (<a title="Guru Article Link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=5:guru&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Guru</a>, <a title="Shukra Article Link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=6:shukra&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Shukra</a>, <a title="Chandra Article Link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=2:chandra&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Chandra</a>) exchange houses then the resultant PY is very good.</p>\r\n<p>3. If two natural malefics (<a title="Surya Article Link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=1:surya&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Surya</a>, <a title="Mangal Article Link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=3:mangal&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Mangal</a>, <a title="Shani Article Link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=7:shani&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Shani</a>, <a title="Rahu Article Link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=8:rahu&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Rahu</a>) exchange houses then the resultant PY is decent.</p>\r\n<p>4. If a natural benefic and natural malefic exchange house then the rusult is somewhat good.</p>\r\n<p>5. If there is PY between lords of <a title="Vishnu Sthana Link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=72:kendra-stahanas&amp;catid=41:main-articles">Vishnu Sthanas</a> then the result is best. It is icing on cake if rule 2 and rule 5 both occur in a horoscope.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>6. If there is PY between lord of Vishnu Sthana and <a title="Laxmi Sthana Link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=85:laxmi-sthanas&amp;catid=41:main-articles">Laxmi Sthana</a> then results are very good.</p>\r\n<p>7. If there is PY between lord of Vishnu Sthana/Laxmi Sthana and Dushamsthana then the result is not as desired.</p>\r\n<p>8. If there is a PY between lords of dushamsthanas then result is good but resultant <a title="Vipreeta Raja Yoga Link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=84:vry&amp;catid=13:imp-yogas&amp;Itemid=113">Vipreeta Raja Yoga</a> gets cancelled.</p>\r\n<p>9. If there is a PY between lords of 1st ,2nd, 4th, 5th, 7th, 9th, 10th, 11th house then results are good but if lord of 3rd house does Parivartana Yoga with any house in horoscope then result are not as desired.</p>\r\n<p>10. PY doesn''t give desired results if the two planets doing Parivartana Yoga are in bad placement in the Navamsha Chart.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Unless there is a Parivartana Yoga between natural benefics, lords of Laxmi Sthanas/Vishnu Sthanas or natural malefics in a dushamsthana the desired results are not observed. There maybe a couple of benefits obtained by the resultant yoga in other locations but native has to work hard to obtain those good results. The very essence of Parivartana Yoga is CHANGE FOR THE BETTER and it can only happen when there is <a title="Purushartha Article Link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=82:purushartha&amp;catid=41:main-articles">Purushartha</a> applied.&nbsp;</p>', 1, '', 0, 1, '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 899, '', '2014-03-25 12:20:40', 899, '2014-03-25 11:22:33', '*', '2014-03-25 11:21:37', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 83, 272, '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 0, 4, 0, 'parivartana yoga, exchange of houses, parivartana between two planets, exchange of houses between planets', 'parivartana yoga', 14, '', 1),
(91, 'com_content.article', 'Gaja Kesari Yoga', 'gky', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; Gaja Kesari Yoga (GKY) is formed when the noble <a title="Guru Article Link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=5:guru&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Guru</a> occupies Vishnu Sthanas from <a title="Chandra Article Link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=2:chandra&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109">Chandra</a> or Ascendant. Gaj means an elephant in sanskrit while Kesari means a lion. There are different interpretations of the meaning of this yoga but what has been observed is the native with such yoga is influential and formidable but at the same time calm, composed, learned and humble with others. In simpler terms he is courageous like a lion but smart and peaceful like an elephant.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Guru in <a title="Vishnu Sthanas Link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=72:kendra-stahanas&amp;catid=41:main-articles">Vishnu Sthanas</a> from Lagna or Chandra is not a big deal. It could happen in a lot of horoscopes. Yet not all of them get the benefits of GKY. What is important is Guru is in kendra in a favorable rashi and not aspected by malefic planets. That happens quit rarely. The best type of GKY is formed when Guru+Chandra are together in Vishnu Sthanas from ascendant and located in Karka Rashi or Meena Rashi. Even Dhana Rashi which belongs to Guru can lessen the effects as it has a fiery nature which doesn''t go well with Chandra who has watery nature. Auspicious placement of Guru+Chandra in a favorable rashi also gives rise to Laxmi Yoga. It is very likely that such natives enjoy full benefits of GKY. GKY doesn''t give expected results if Guru is in Makara Rashi, aspected by enemy planets or bereft of strength.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Simplest way to find if there is indeed a GKY is to look at the native himself. If he is rich and posseses all comforts from birth and by nature he is calm, good mannered, good cultured and religious then rest assured there is likely to be GKY or some sort of Guru+Chandra associations. This is one of the few yogas which gives results from inception and doesn''t need time to fructify.&nbsp;</p>', 1, '', 0, 1, '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 899, '', '2014-03-25 12:23:25', 899, '2014-03-25 11:24:52', '*', '2014-03-25 11:24:12', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 84, 274, '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 0, 3, 0, 'gaja kesari yoga, laxmi yoga, yogas for wealth, guru chandra yoga, guru-chandra yoga', 'gaja kesari yoga description', 14, '', 1),
(92, 'com_content.article', 'Laxmi Sthanas', 'laxmi', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Laxmi Sthanas are the trine consisting of <a title="1st house link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=10:tanu-bhava&amp;catid=10:12-houses&amp;Itemid=114">1st house</a>, <a title="5th house link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=14:putra-bhava&amp;catid=10:12-houses&amp;Itemid=110">5th house</a> and <a title="9th house link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=18:bhagya-sthana&amp;catid=10:12-houses&amp;Itemid=110">9th house</a>. They are also known as Trikon Sthana (Triangle Houses). Ironically all the 3 concerned houses rule Dharma. Goddess Laxmi is the wife of Lord Vishnu and goddess of wealth and prosperity. She is also the overseer of fortune and luck.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;There is a catch to the name Laxmi Sthanas. 1st house represents character and moral values, 5th house represents knowledge and wisdom and 9th house represents faith and religion. Those who have a good moral values, possess knowledge and wisdom as well as practice faith and religion are said to gain wealth and prosperity. All the 3 houses rule Dharma so in a way, it can be said that wealth and prosperity comes to those who practice Dharma.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;From an astrological perspective Laxmi Sthanas determine fame, fortune and luck. If the house lords of Laxmi Sthanas form Parivartana Yoga or located in Vishnu Sthanas then the concerned native is lucky and famous in life. If the house lords of Laxmi Sthanas are in dushamsthanas or debilitated then native maybe bereft of fame and fortune.&nbsp;</p>', 1, '', 0, 1, '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 899, '', '2014-03-25 12:28:14', 899, '2014-03-25 11:31:35', '*', '2014-03-25 11:29:19', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 85, 276, '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 0, 4, 0, 'vedic astrology, laxmi sthanas, trikona sthanas, dharma sthanas, dharma houses', 'laxmi sthana in astrology', 19, '', 1),
(93, 'com_content.article', 'Vishnu Sthanas', 'vishnu', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Vishnu Sthanas also known as Kendra Sthanas are the quadrant of <a title="Navigate to article on 1st house" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=10:tanu-bhava&amp;catid=10:12-houses&amp;Itemid=114">1st house</a>, <a title="4th house article" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=13:matru-bhava&amp;catid=10:12-houses&amp;Itemid=110">4th house</a>, <a title="7th house article" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=16:kalatra-bhava&amp;catid=10:12-houses&amp;Itemid=110">7th house</a> and <a title="10th house article" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=19:karma-bhava&amp;catid=10:12-houses&amp;Itemid=110">10th house</a> respectively. Each of them rules an important aspect of life''s goal. 1st house provides Dharma, 10th house provides Artha, 7th house provides Kama while 4th house provides Moksha.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;There is a reason why this houses are named as Vishnu Sthanas. Lord Vishnu is called the Palanhaar or Provider. He is charged with the duty of providing basic amenities of life to the people to survive. In similar manner the 4 houses of Vishnu Sthanas are charged with providing the basic amenities of life for survival. 1st house provides health and character, 4th house provides education, nurturing and shelter, 7th house provides progeny and partner to reach higher conscious and 10th house provides fame, popularity and social standing.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; In vedic astrology if there is strength in Vishnu Sthanas it is observed that all the evils in Dushamsthanas or other house can produce no harm to the native. If none of the 4 houses in Vishnu Sthana have strength then native cannot make anything out of himself no matter how hard he tries. Most of the auspicious yoga involve Vishnu Sthanas in one way or other.&nbsp;</p>', 1, '', 0, 1, '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 899, '', '2014-03-25 12:32:14', 899, '2014-03-25 11:33:56', '*', '2014-03-25 11:33:19', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 86, 278, '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', 0, 3, 0, 'vishnu sthanas, kendra houses, vedic astrology, astrology tutorials', 'vishnu sthanas in astrology', 19, '', 1);
