(362, 41, 1, '', '2014-03-06 11:30:24', 899, 5748, '95e80d2864a206857cce86be9f8f6d02cdd71805', '{"id":41,"asset_id":"160","title":"Pushya","alias":"pushya","introtext":"<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Pushya nakshatra is the eight nakshatra among the <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=category&amp;id=12&amp;Itemid=112\\">27 nakshatras<\\/a>&nbsp;in Vedic Astrology. The word ''Pushya'' means nourishment and accordingly this nakshatra replenishes, nourishes and reinvigorates. Pushya is regarded as the best among the 27 nakshatras. All the auspicious undertakings or purchase of jewelry are done when <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=2:chandra&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109\\">Chandra<\\/a> enters Pushya Nakshatra. Pushya is ruled by <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=7:shani&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109\\">shani<\\/a> and its symbol is cow''s udder. The gana is devta and the presiding deity is Brihaspati or <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=5:guru&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109\\">Guru<\\/a>. All the 4 Padas of Pushya are in <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=25:karka&amp;catid=11:12-signs&amp;Itemid=111\\">Karka<\\/a> rashi.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Physical Features: Pushya natives are difficult to discern based on physical characteristics. Since the nakshatra is ruled by Shani, situated in Karka which is Chandra''s rashi and presiding diety is Guru a lot of anomalies are seen in physical traits. Sometimes males are observed to be tall and thin while woman are noticed to be short with an oval face.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Character\\/Events: Pushya natives are hard working and dedicated to their work. They have a helping nature. The nakshatra of Shani brings control and organization in life of natives through difficult circumstances in early childhood. Poverty is possible upto 15 or 16 years of life. Generally hardships and dependency in early life moulds pushya natives character and they become independent, organized, hard working, sincere and honest individuals. They can work with patience and calm towards achievement of a goal. Careful consideration is required to not overtake a business or project without careful thinking otherwise the desired result may not be ideal. As the natives learn more through experience it is not necessary for them to opt for a difficult course. Hard work and dedication often makes them over burdened at work place. Extra care is required not to overdo things and concentrate on doing the task allocated without getting into the nitty gritty details. As long as skills and abilities are assessed before proceding to work, nothing shall be impossible for the natives. Another impeccable quality is their honesty which does not let them take criminal or illegal tasks. Females apart from qualities mentioned above have peaceful and submissive nature. Pushya natives both males and females cannot properly handle negative criticism or positive feedback.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Family life- Pushya natives are quite attached to their parents. They become independent when they grow up. Spouse for pushya males natives should be self sufficient and with a conservative thinking, dress sense. Females are submissive and cannot express themselves freely. This leads partners to doubt them. Females are devoted and amicable by nature. Both male and female natives have a problem with expressing themselves due to Shani (restrictions) ruling the rashi of Chandra which controls emotions they have difficulties in family life. Many a times natives have to live away from family.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Positives: Hard working, help others, good advisers, honest, dedicated and liked by others.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Negatives: Insecure, Problems in expressing themselves, dogmatic, over sensitive<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Health: Shani is dry and cold while Chandra rules all the bodily fluids. Thereby problems related to body fluids like hormonal problems, cough, cold, asthma or other problems related to Kapha Dosha are possible.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Remedies: Praying to Lord Vishnu is advised for pushya natives.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"13","created":"2014-02-02 02:22:16","created_by":"899","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2014-03-06 11:30:24","modified_by":"899","checked_out":"899","checked_out_time":"2014-03-06 11:29:30","publish_up":"2014-02-02 02:22:16","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_author\\":\\"\\",\\"link_author\\":\\"\\",\\"show_create_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_modify_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publish_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_item_navigation\\":\\"\\",\\"show_icons\\":\\"\\",\\"show_print_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_email_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_vote\\":\\"\\",\\"show_hits\\":\\"\\",\\"show_noauth\\":\\"\\",\\"urls_position\\":\\"\\",\\"alternative_readmore\\":\\"\\",\\"article_layout\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publishing_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_article_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_backend\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\":\\"\\"}","version":4,"ordering":"20","metakey":"nakshatra ruled by shani, pushya nakshatra, 27 nakshatras","metadesc":"pushya nakshatra in vedic astrology","access":"1","hits":"0","metadata":"{\\"robots\\":\\"\\",\\"author\\":\\"\\",\\"rights\\":\\"\\",\\"xreference\\":\\"\\"}","featured":"0","language":"*","xreference":""}', 0),
(363, 42, 1, '', '2014-03-06 11:34:59', 899, 4870, '3105026ca48e81c636a9d0d8ea2522f4a98adead', '{"id":42,"asset_id":"162","title":"Ashlesha","alias":"ashlesha","introtext":"<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Ashlesha is the ninth nakshatra among the <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=category&amp;id=12&amp;Itemid=112\\">27 nakshatra<\\/a> studied in Vedic Astrology. It is ruled by <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=4:buddh&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109\\">Budh<\\/a>&nbsp;and all the 4 Padas are located in <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=25:karka&amp;catid=11:12-signs&amp;Itemid=111\\">Karka<\\/a> rashi. The symbol for Ashlesha is a coiled snake and presiding diety is Naga. According to Valmiki Ramayan the twin brothers Laxman and Shatrughan were born in this nakshatra.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Physical Features: Natives have a pentrating glare which can hyponitize and mesmerize its prey, very much like a snake. Also they have an intriguing speech and a way with words. They have a stout body and brownish complexion. They do not have much resistance power. Looks are not the most attractive either.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Character\\/Events: Natives have to accept responsibility at a very young age due to parents not alive or abandoning the native. This makes the native very possesive in nature for other relationship as he can''t stand the sight to lose them. Inspite of emotional insecurities the natives can be quite self-centred. They make quite good politicians with their mezmerizing body language and attractive speeches. Ofcourse Ashlesha natives are more associated with cunning, deceit and corrupt so you rarely see honest administrators in this nakshatra. They are often deceitful and can be quite cruel sometimes. Native is emotionally insecure and seldom suffer from mental diseases like schizophrenia and paranoia. Too much of suspicion in life invites all sorts of mental worries. While they are open to criticizing others they do not welcome personal criticism. Career in Politics, as a Physician, Psychologist, Applied Medicines, Chemical Engineer, Chemist and in Sex Rackets is possible.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Family Life: Often abandoned by parents at early age when Ashlesha nakshatra is in lagna. Chandra in ashlesha makes a native insecure and sometimes leads to suspicion and worries. Natives over possessive nature becomes a problem in relationship. Chandra in ashlesha makes a native insecure and sometimes leads to suspicion and worries. Native is not able to give the space needed for a relationship to thrive Too much criticism and poisonous tongue can also damage relationship. Unable to co-exist in surrounding environment.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Positives: Intelligent, Learned, Mesmerizing, Leadership Qualities.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Negatives: Mental Instability, Deceitful, Possessive, Secretive and Talkative.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Health: Mental disease are possible for Ashlesha natives. Also flatulence and stomach problems possible.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Remedies: For the suspicious nature, poisonous tongue and mental insecurities praying to Lord Shiva is best. To calm the talkative and manipulative nature prayers to Lord Ram or Lord Vishnu are advised.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"13","created":"2014-02-02 02:23:50","created_by":"899","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2014-03-06 11:34:59","modified_by":"899","checked_out":"899","checked_out_time":"2014-03-06 11:33:51","publish_up":"2014-02-02 02:23:50","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_author\\":\\"\\",\\"link_author\\":\\"\\",\\"show_create_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_modify_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publish_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_item_navigation\\":\\"\\",\\"show_icons\\":\\"\\",\\"show_print_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_email_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_vote\\":\\"\\",\\"show_hits\\":\\"\\",\\"show_noauth\\":\\"\\",\\"urls_position\\":\\"\\",\\"alternative_readmore\\":\\"\\",\\"article_layout\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publishing_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_article_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_backend\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\":\\"\\"}","version":3,"ordering":"18","metakey":"ashlesha nakshatra, 27 nakshatras, nakshatras ruled by mercury, nakshatras ruled by buddh","metadesc":"ashlesha nakshatra in vedic astrology","access":"1","hits":"0","metadata":"{\\"robots\\":\\"\\",\\"author\\":\\"\\",\\"rights\\":\\"\\",\\"xreference\\":\\"\\"}","featured":"0","language":"*","xreference":""}', 0),
(364, 43, 1, '', '2014-03-06 11:43:02', 899, 5324, 'd33aac3e2edd44affedbda76ff3d2d5f540034e2', '{"id":43,"asset_id":"164","title":"Magha","alias":"magha","introtext":"<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Magha is the tenth nakshatra among the <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=category&amp;id=12&amp;Itemid=112\\">27 Nakshatras<\\/a> studied in Vedic Astrology. All the 4 Padas of Magha are situated in the rashi of <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=26:simha&amp;catid=11:12-signs&amp;Itemid=111\\">Simha<\\/a> (ruled by Surya) and Magha is ruled by Ketu. In accordance with it Magha natives have qualities of both Surya and Ketu endowed. Magha''s symbol is a royal throne which symbolizes power, status and prestige. Magha''s gana is Daitya\\/Rakshasha while its presiding diety are the forefathers. Surya''s placement in Magha between 1\\u00b0 and 10\\u00b0 (\\u00b0 = degree) indicates it is in its Mool Trikona position. This placement makes Surya feel like an emperor which can grant gifts and benediction. Magha comes under the category of Ganda Moola Nakshatra.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Character\\/Events: Magha natives are endowed with qualities of both <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=1:surya&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109\\">Surya<\\/a> and <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=9:ketu&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109\\">Ketu<\\/a>. Magha natives are powerful, influential and short tempered. But at the same time they are spiritual and quite generous. Magha natives are optimistic and free spirited. Magha natives obtain fame which can last through generations. Magha females have a frank and courageous nature. At the same time they are charming and have an interesting personality. These qualities invite many fr-enemies. Female natives love their family and can go to any lengths to safeguard their families interest. Such actions can be used by fr-enemies against Magha Females.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Males have a proud and arrogant nature and command respect from their peers. Public status and financial dignity are generally secure for magha natives. Magha natives respect their elders and are god fearing. They are generous and donate money for noble causes and philanthropic activities. Although Magha natives achieve quite good status and wealth they are better off not to pursue an individual business. Their straight forward nature and generous character can lead to loss making in business. This applies for both male and female natives born with <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=2:chandra&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109\\">Chandra<\\/a> in Magha. Magha natives are the ideal middle man or coordinators in work place. Career in top management position is a good option. Also career in politics, law and career as coordinators and brokers is viable.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Family Life: Magha males have good and faithful wife. Females are religious minded and devoted to their husbands. Inspite of that their simple and straight forward nature invites frictions in marriage and family life. Even in the modern day world there are places where woman raising her voice and giving a frank opinion is not invited. Normally both male and female natives have very few friends.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Health: Magha natives may suffer from burns, boils and piles. Night blindness and eye problems are also a possibility.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Positives: Intelligent, Dependable and Smooth Coordinators<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Negatives: Arrogant, Hot Tempered, Susceptible to Criticism and Flattery.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Remedies: Performing religious yagnas and Shradha for obtaining blessings of forefathers.&nbsp;<\\/p>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"13","created":"2014-02-02 02:24:19","created_by":"899","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2014-03-06 11:43:02","modified_by":"899","checked_out":"899","checked_out_time":"2014-03-06 11:42:22","publish_up":"2014-02-02 02:24:19","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_author\\":\\"\\",\\"link_author\\":\\"\\",\\"show_create_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_modify_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publish_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_item_navigation\\":\\"\\",\\"show_icons\\":\\"\\",\\"show_print_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_email_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_vote\\":\\"\\",\\"show_hits\\":\\"\\",\\"show_noauth\\":\\"\\",\\"urls_position\\":\\"\\",\\"alternative_readmore\\":\\"\\",\\"article_layout\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publishing_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_article_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_backend\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\":\\"\\"}","version":3,"ordering":"17","metakey":"magha nakshatra, 27 nakshatra, ganda moola nakshatra, nakshatra ruled by ketu","metadesc":"magha nakshatra in vedic astrology","access":"1","hits":"0","metadata":"{\\"robots\\":\\"\\",\\"author\\":\\"\\",\\"rights\\":\\"\\",\\"xreference\\":\\"\\"}","featured":"0","language":"*","xreference":""}', 0),
(365, 44, 1, '', '2014-03-06 11:44:38', 899, 5337, 'f67f524a40ce25bf0dfd9a53df950453b68167fd', '{"id":44,"asset_id":"166","title":"Purva Phalguni","alias":"purva-phalguni","introtext":"<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Purva Phalguni is the eleventh nakshatra among the <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=category&amp;id=12&amp;Itemid=112\\">27 Nakshatras<\\/a> in Vedic Astrology. All the 4 Padas of Purva Phalguni are in <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=26:simha&amp;catid=11:12-signs&amp;Itemid=111\\">Simha<\\/a> rashi and the ruling planet is Shukra. Gana is Manushya\\/Human and the Presiding diety is <a href=\\"http:\\/\\/en.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/Bhaga\\" target=\\"_blank\\">Bhaga<\\/a> who is one of the <a href=\\"http:\\/\\/en.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/%C4%80dityas\\" target=\\"_blank\\">12 Adityas<\\/a>. Symbol for Purva Phalguni is a swinging hammock (Jhula).<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;This nakshatra is called Bhagadaivata Star. All the good things in life like pleasure, prosperity, love, enjoyment and sensual blessings are possible through blessings of this nakshatra. A nakshatra ruled by <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=6:shukra&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109\\">Shukra<\\/a> in the rashi of <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=1:surya&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109\\">Surya<\\/a> is precipice for good fortune, luck and prosperity.&nbsp;<span style=\\"color: #333333; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;\\"><span><br \\/><\\/span><\\/span><span>&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Physical Features: Purva Phalguni females have an oval face and well built figure. They are soft and cultured but prone to arrogance. Males have a healthy constitution, attractive personality and mixed color. Purva Phalguni Natives both males and females are energetic and restless.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Character\\/Events: Natives have a strong desire to be liked and noticed by others. They are fond of music and arts. They generally avoid conflicts and disputes and try to solve conflicts peacefully through tact. Natives like to travel to places where weather is clear and bright like sunny beaches or mountains. Natives enjoy freedom and do not like working under subordination. If employed at a workplace, the tend to change their jobs frequently until 45 years of age. Period after 45 years of age sees power and authority. They generally oppose to getting benefits at the cost of others. Natives like to be clean and tidy. Purva Phalguni natives are better off with starting their own business venture or earning an independent livelihood through arts or music. It is difficult for natives to learn new things as their scope is limited to earning fame and fortune. Career as Actors, Models, Musicians, Retail Sales, Travel Agents, Cosmetics, Jewelry, Wedding Planners, Sex Therapist and Marriage Counselor is possible.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Family Life: Both male and female natives enjoy happiness and enjoyment in married life. Both the life partner and children provide happiness to individuals. Love marriage is more likely compared to arranged marriage. Native resides away from birth place and family members. Purva Phalguni natives have a good circle of friends and are quite popular in their group. Extra-marital affairs is a possible scenario for Purva Phalguni natives.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Positives: Creative, Intelligent, Charming, Carefree, Open Minded, Refined, Youthful<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Negatives: Indulgent, Impulsive, Promiscuous Nature, Narcissism.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Health: Dental problems are possible.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Remedies: Prayers to Goddess Laxmi. Seva and Pooja of Shiva Linga is also beneficial.&nbsp;<\\/p>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"13","created":"2014-02-02 02:25:41","created_by":"899","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2014-03-06 11:44:38","modified_by":"899","checked_out":"899","checked_out_time":"2014-03-06 11:43:36","publish_up":"2014-02-02 02:25:41","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_author\\":\\"\\",\\"link_author\\":\\"\\",\\"show_create_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_modify_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publish_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_item_navigation\\":\\"\\",\\"show_icons\\":\\"\\",\\"show_print_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_email_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_vote\\":\\"\\",\\"show_hits\\":\\"\\",\\"show_noauth\\":\\"\\",\\"urls_position\\":\\"\\",\\"alternative_readmore\\":\\"\\",\\"article_layout\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publishing_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_article_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_backend\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\":\\"\\"}","version":5,"ordering":"16","metakey":"purvaphalguni nakshatra, purva phalguni nakshatra, nakshatra ruled by shukra, nakshatra ruled by venus","metadesc":"purva phalguni nakshatra in vedic astrology","access":"1","hits":"0","metadata":"{\\"robots\\":\\"\\",\\"author\\":\\"\\",\\"rights\\":\\"\\",\\"xreference\\":\\"\\"}","featured":"0","language":"*","xreference":""}', 0),
(366, 45, 1, '', '2014-03-06 11:51:43', 899, 5146, 'e3ac2528508d812e8fc7d3cc8b246750db91ac05', '{"id":45,"asset_id":"168","title":"Uttara Phalguni","alias":"uttara-phalguni","introtext":"<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Uttara Phalguni is the twelfth nakshatra among the <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=category&amp;id=12&amp;Itemid=112\\">27 Nakshatras<\\/a> studied in Vedic Astrology. The gana for Uttara Phalguni is Manushya\\/Human while the ruling planet is <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=1:surya&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109\\">Surya<\\/a>. Presiding diety is <a href=\\"http:\\/\\/en.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/Aryaman\\" target=\\"_blank\\">Aryaman<\\/a> and the symbol is a bed. The 1st Pada of this nakshatra is located in <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=26:simha&amp;catid=11:12-signs&amp;Itemid=111\\">Simha<\\/a> rashi while the remaining 3 Padas are located in <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=27:kanya&amp;catid=11:12-signs&amp;Itemid=111\\">Kanya<\\/a> rashi. In accordance the natives with <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=2:chandra&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109\\">Chandra<\\/a> in 1st Pada show characteristics of Surya like arrogance, leadership skills and intolerant nature while the natives with Chandra in the remaining 3 Padas show characteristics of <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=4:buddh&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109\\">Budh<\\/a> like chatty and articulate nature.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Physical Features; Natives of Uttara Phalguni have some sort of prominent mark like black mole on neck or face. Male natives are tall and chubby with large face and long nose. Women born in Uttara Phalguni have a soft voice. Natives born in 1st Pada of Uttara Phalguni have good health and eyesight as well as attractive eyes.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Character\\/Events: Uttara Phalguni natives are born social workers. They are quite helpful to their friends, family and generally to all in need. While natives of the 1st Pada maybe arrogant and proud due to the combination of Surya Nakshatra (Uttara Phalguni ) + Surya rashi (<a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=26:simha&amp;catid=11:12-signs&amp;Itemid=111\\">Simha<\\/a>), the natives born in other 3 Padas are simple and straight forward. While natives of 1st Pada maybe irritating they do get high position in life. It has been observed that females can make quite a good career as actress if they are born when 1st Pada of Uttara Phalguni is in lagna\\/ascendent. Natives of 1st Pada are hot tempered while the natives of other 3 Padas which fall in Kanya rashi resolve conflicts through discussion. Uttara Phalguni natives often see meaningful progress after 38 years of life have passed. Uttara Phalguni natives can have wonderful career as Social Worker, Philantrophist, Actors, Mathematician, Astrologers and Astronomers.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Family Life: Generally for male natives in Uttara Phalguni married life possesses little or no friction. Women can get a good partner and children. Women are good in managing matters of domestic life.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Positives: Ambitious, Good Communicator, Generous<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Negatives: Ego, Stubborn and Over-giving<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Health: Health remains good with no major complications unless some bad placement in horoscope is present.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Remedies: Praying to Surya and chanting of the Gayatri Mantra.&nbsp;<\\/p>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"13","created":"2014-02-02 02:26:26","created_by":"899","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2014-03-06 11:51:43","modified_by":"899","checked_out":"899","checked_out_time":"2014-03-06 11:49:45","publish_up":"2014-02-02 02:26:26","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_author\\":\\"\\",\\"link_author\\":\\"\\",\\"show_create_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_modify_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publish_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_item_navigation\\":\\"\\",\\"show_icons\\":\\"\\",\\"show_print_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_email_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_vote\\":\\"\\",\\"show_hits\\":\\"\\",\\"show_noauth\\":\\"\\",\\"urls_position\\":\\"\\",\\"alternative_readmore\\":\\"\\",\\"article_layout\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publishing_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_article_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_backend\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\":\\"\\"}","version":3,"ordering":"15","metakey":"uttaraphalguni nakshatra, uttara phalguni nakshatra, nakshatra ruled by surya, nakshatra ruled by sun","metadesc":"uttara phalguni nakshatra in vedic astrology","access":"1","hits":"0","metadata":"{\\"robots\\":\\"\\",\\"author\\":\\"\\",\\"rights\\":\\"\\",\\"xreference\\":\\"\\"}","featured":"0","language":"*","xreference":""}', 0),
(367, 46, 1, '', '2014-03-06 11:52:57', 899, 4925, '963f3e516360856caf411b0998422411abca4213', '{"id":46,"asset_id":"170","title":"Hasta","alias":"hasta","introtext":"<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Hasta is the the thirteenth nakshatra among the <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=category&amp;id=12&amp;Itemid=112\\">27 nakshatras<\\/a> studied in Vedic Astrology. All the 4 Padas are located in <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=27:kanya&amp;catid=11:12-signs&amp;Itemid=111\\">Kanya<\\/a> rashi. The gana is devta and the presiding diety is <a href=\\"http:\\/\\/en.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/Savitr\\" target=\\"_blank\\">Savitr<\\/a> who is one of the 12 Adityas. Hasta Nakshatra is ruled by <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=2:chandra&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109\\">Chandra<\\/a> and located in the rashi of <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=4:buddh&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109\\">Budh<\\/a>. This awkward Budh-Chandra relationship can sometimes cause nervous disorders as Budh (rules the nervous system) and Chandra (rules the mind and thoughts) are planetary enemies.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Physical Appearance: Female natives can be chubby with a fat stomach and prominent chest region. Males though typically less attractive make up with an attractive personality. Both male and female natives could be tall with scar on upper right hand or below shoulders.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Character\\/Events: Hasta females have a warm but lazy character. Hasta females only work when required but handle task cheerfully and with energy. Female natives are generally cheerful and do not stay angry for long. Hasta males are clever, witty and entertaining. They like to keep company of females. Hasta natives of both gender are a great company to have. Natives are unable to adapt to new technology and thoughts and prefer the old traditions and customs. Hasta natives get respect and honor from public. There is a possibility for fluctuations in life through mental, physical and social factors.&nbsp; Moderate success is observed for natives with&nbsp; help coming from unexpected quarters. Natives are better to pursue a career in business and can make good advisers. A good all round knowledge is observed in the natives and capability to solve disputes peacefully is a trait among natives. Period from 30 to 42 years is golden period of life. Career as craftsmen, Artist, Writers, Painters, Teachers, Adviser, Volunteer Work. Hospital Staff, Counselors, Astrologer, Travel Industry and Comedians is possible.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Family Life: Hasta natives have a tendency to give parental guidance especially in a relationship. They do not see their partner as their equal but rather someone who needs parenting. Marriage for Hasta Natives is more satisfying in later years. Partner is simple and capable. No major problems are indicated in married life unless there are other bad planetary combinations or aspect.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Health: Natives may suffer from bad health especially cough and cold. Females may also suffer from rheumatism and piles.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Positives: Creative, Humorous, Practical and Pleasant Personality<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Negatives: Emotional instability and Bad Health<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Remedies: Hasta natives should pray to Surya.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"13","created":"2014-02-02 02:26:57","created_by":"899","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2014-03-06 11:52:57","modified_by":"899","checked_out":"899","checked_out_time":"2014-03-06 11:52:05","publish_up":"2014-02-02 02:26:57","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_author\\":\\"\\",\\"link_author\\":\\"\\",\\"show_create_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_modify_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publish_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_item_navigation\\":\\"\\",\\"show_icons\\":\\"\\",\\"show_print_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_email_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_vote\\":\\"\\",\\"show_hits\\":\\"\\",\\"show_noauth\\":\\"\\",\\"urls_position\\":\\"\\",\\"alternative_readmore\\":\\"\\",\\"article_layout\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publishing_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_article_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_backend\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\":\\"\\"}","version":3,"ordering":"14","metakey":"hasta nakshatra, 27 nakshatras, nakshatra ruled by chandra","metadesc":"hasta nakshatra in vedic astrology","access":"1","hits":"0","metadata":"{\\"robots\\":\\"\\",\\"author\\":\\"\\",\\"rights\\":\\"\\",\\"xreference\\":\\"\\"}","featured":"0","language":"*","xreference":""}', 0),
(368, 47, 1, '', '2014-03-06 11:54:46', 899, 5341, 'fb6a476871125e0a8210e984e450e100bd317b98', '{"id":47,"asset_id":"172","title":"Chitra","alias":"chitra","introtext":"<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Chitra Nakshatra is the fourteenth nakshatra among the <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=category&amp;id=12&amp;Itemid=112\\">27 Nakshatras<\\/a> in Vedic Astrology. The first 3 Padas are located in <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=27:kanya&amp;catid=11:12-signs&amp;Itemid=111\\">Kanya rashi<\\/a> while the fourth and last pada is located in <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=28:tula&amp;catid=11:12-signs&amp;Itemid=111\\">Tula rashi<\\/a>. The gana for Chitra is Daitya while the symbol is an oyster with a pearl in it. <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=3:mangal&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109\\">Mangal<\\/a> is the ruling planet for Chitra nakshatra and the presiding diety is Vishwakarma who is the god of all creation. Ideally a nakshatra of warrior Mangal in the rashi of talkative <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=4:buddh&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109\\">Budh<\\/a> or extravagant <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=6:shukra&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109\\">Shukra<\\/a> is not ideal. Yet this natives learn with time and gain extraordinary success especially those born with <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=2:chandra&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109\\">Chandra<\\/a> in Kanya rashi. Chitra lagna is considered auspicious for males but inauspicious for females.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Physical Features: Chitra natives have a lean body. They maybe stout and tall sometimes.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Character\\/Events: Chitra males are clever, successful, dexterous and direct in speech. Females are fickle with men, competitive and even selfish in some cases. Chitra females with Chandra in Tula rashi are expensive and luxurious. They are fond of perfumes, cosmetics and expensive items. Extra marital relationship is possible due to the Mangal+Shukra relationship. Chitra females born with Chandra in Kanya are a bit masculine and athletic.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Chitra males are thoughful and profound in approach. They are great with machines and tools be it mechanical or surgical equipments. Kanya born chitra natives are creative while Tula born chitra natives are more artistic and like music, acting etc. Period between 33 years and 54 years of age will be golden period for native. Chitra natives are fantastic planners. They have ideal career as Software or Hardware Professionals. They can also make good surgeons. In addition they can make a successful career in army planning and intelligence, real estate developers and tula born natives can also become actors, designers and musicians.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Family Life: Natives derive love and respect from their siblings and parents but sometimes difference of opinion is possible with family members. Generally Chitra natives live separate from home and family members. Native enjoy a great repo with mother and get gains from mothers relatives. Married life is not cordial and frictions are possible. Though divorce is unlikely unless other inauspicious yoga are present.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Health: Difficulty in internal organs especially kidneys and bladder as well as tumors and appendicitis.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Positives: Artistic, Independent, Innovative Thinkers and Intelligent Planners<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Negatives: Quarrelsome, Critical (in kanya rashi), Immoral and Spendthrift (in tula rashi)<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Remedies: Praying to Goddess Durga.&nbsp;<\\/p>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"13","created":"2014-02-02 02:27:26","created_by":"899","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2014-03-06 11:54:46","modified_by":"899","checked_out":"899","checked_out_time":"2014-03-06 11:53:50","publish_up":"2014-02-02 02:27:26","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_author\\":\\"\\",\\"link_author\\":\\"\\",\\"show_create_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_modify_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publish_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_item_navigation\\":\\"\\",\\"show_icons\\":\\"\\",\\"show_print_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_email_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_vote\\":\\"\\",\\"show_hits\\":\\"\\",\\"show_noauth\\":\\"\\",\\"urls_position\\":\\"\\",\\"alternative_readmore\\":\\"\\",\\"article_layout\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publishing_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_article_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_backend\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\":\\"\\"}","version":3,"ordering":"13","metakey":"chitra nakshatra, 27 nakshatras, vedic astrology, nakshatra ruled by mangal, nakshatra ruled by mars","metadesc":"chitra nakshatra in vedic astrology","access":"1","hits":"0","metadata":"{\\"robots\\":\\"\\",\\"author\\":\\"\\",\\"rights\\":\\"\\",\\"xreference\\":\\"\\"}","featured":"0","language":"*","xreference":""}', 0),
(369, 48, 1, '', '2014-03-06 11:56:08', 899, 4503, 'd707e1929725ec055703f51ccd91050aca41bf82', '{"id":48,"asset_id":"174","title":"Swati","alias":"swati","introtext":"<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Swati is the fifteenth nakshatra among the <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=category&amp;id=12&amp;Itemid=112\\">27 Nakshatras<\\/a> studied in Vedic Astrology. Swati is ruled by <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=8:rahu&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109\\">Rahu<\\/a> and the presiding deity is Vayu. All the 4 Padas are located in Tula rashi and the gana for swati is devta. Though Tula rashi is the rashi of balance, Rahu creates imbalance and unrest in the lives of Swati natives. Unless <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=7:shani&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109\\">Shani<\\/a> is involved the inner feelings and outer behavior of Swati natives tends to be poles apart.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Physical Features: Natives both males and females are attractive and alluring. Females have a distinguished speech and manner of walking.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Character &amp; Events: Swati natives have mysterious behavior. The outward calm and composed demeanor due to Tula Rashi''s balanced persona is hindered by the inner turmoil and uneasy feelings brought forth by Rahu who always wants more. Swati natives cannot stay at one place and like to travel as and when they please. While Rahu encourages taboo breaking activities which are anti-social and unlawful the balancing view of Tula rarely allows that side to be in public view. They may be enticed to pursue taboo activities in secret but outwardly they love to show simplicity and good mannerisms. Generally Swati females have a truthful and straight forward character. While males are thoughtful and slow in their actions they are brilliant at analyzing work based on intelligence and logic. Swati males are religious and somewhat orthodox. Swati natives are peace loving but prone to be hot tempered and revengeful when instigated. They are adamant in their views and independent in their approach. They do not level criticism at others and cannot handle criticism leveled at them. Period after 30 years sees growth in business and professional sector. Swati natives have ideal career in travelling sector, pharmacist, diplomats, gold smith and politicians (if Shani is involved).<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Family Life: Swati natives do not have an ideal married life. While the outer picture is a happy married life the inner reality is different. Native may have no stability in matters of money and place of accommodation.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Health: Mysterious conditions possible due to Swati being a nakshatra of Rahu.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Positives: Business Minded, Friendly, Independent.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Negatives: Hot Temper<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Remedies: Swati natives should pray to Saraswati and Bhairav (Avatar of Rudra). &nbsp;<\\/p>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"13","created":"2014-02-02 02:30:30","created_by":"899","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2014-03-06 11:56:08","modified_by":"899","checked_out":"899","checked_out_time":"2014-03-06 11:55:02","publish_up":"2014-02-02 02:30:30","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_author\\":\\"\\",\\"link_author\\":\\"\\",\\"show_create_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_modify_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publish_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_item_navigation\\":\\"\\",\\"show_icons\\":\\"\\",\\"show_print_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_email_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_vote\\":\\"\\",\\"show_hits\\":\\"\\",\\"show_noauth\\":\\"\\",\\"urls_position\\":\\"\\",\\"alternative_readmore\\":\\"\\",\\"article_layout\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publishing_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_article_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_backend\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\":\\"\\"}","version":5,"ordering":"12","metakey":"swati nakshatra, 27 nakshatra, nakshatra ruled by rahu","metadesc":"swati nakshatra in vedic astrology","access":"1","hits":"0","metadata":"{\\"robots\\":\\"\\",\\"author\\":\\"\\",\\"rights\\":\\"\\",\\"xreference\\":\\"\\"}","featured":"0","language":"*","xreference":""}', 0),
(370, 49, 1, '', '2014-03-06 11:59:41', 899, 5512, 'ff0eb9f049f4b7f7358dbd4a56245d91c1583c55', '{"id":49,"asset_id":"176","title":"Vishakha","alias":"vishakha","introtext":"<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Vishakha Nakshatra is the sixteenth nakshatra among <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=category&amp;id=12&amp;Itemid=112\\">27 Nakshatras<\\/a> in Vedic Astrology. While the first 3 Padas are located in <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=28:tula&amp;catid=11:12-signs&amp;Itemid=111\\">Tula Rashi<\\/a> the last pada of Vishakha is in <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=29:vrischika&amp;catid=11:12-signs&amp;Itemid=111\\">Vrischika Rashi<\\/a>. The presiding diety for Vishakha are Indra and Agni while the gana is Rakhshasa. The ruling planet is the benevolent <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=5:guru&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109\\">Guru<\\/a>. Vishakha is also called Anuradha which is the birth star of <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=1:surya&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109\\">Surya<\\/a> while it is also called Radha who is known as the consort of Lord Krishna. Vishakha has the nature of its deities Indra and Agni which is full of splendor and vigor albeit for a short period of time.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Physical Features: Vishakha natives are round, bright and physical appearance is attractive. Some natives are obese and tall while others have a short and lean structure. Vishaksha females have delicate features and a soft and pleasing voice but underneath the delicacy likes a very strong character.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Character &amp; Events: Vishakha natives are full of vigor and vitality and possess intelligence of the highest order. They are firm believers in God but do not believe in orthodox principles or age old traditions. They are fond of adopting modern ideas. They treat all religion, caste and creed as equal. Vishakha natives are also impatient, aggressive and quite quarrelsome. They are quite active but not so much popular. Their aggressive behavior is disliked by others. Also they have lot of pride and are easily offended. They may have enemies due to hot temper and arrogant nature. Natives born in Tula rashi in the first 3 Padas have strong diplomatic skills. Natives sometimes are spendthrift while other times they are stingy in spending. Vishakha natives are best advised to do independent business or high responsibility jobs. Career as Psychologist, Medical Diagnosis, Counseling, Investigative Journalism and Scientific Research is best suited. Due to good oratary skill natives could also be good Politicians.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Family Life: Vishakha females are quite appealing to opposite sex and generally have a fortunate marriage. Husband is good natured and wealthy. Female natives are likely to have very few children. Female natives are fond of travels and travel often with their partners. Vishakha natives have more enemies as compared to friends. Vishakha natives do not get appropriate love or care from mother owing to death of mother or other unforseen circumstances. Although they respect their father very much and father also is the more doting of the two parents there are bound to be differences with father. This makes the natives hard working and self made individuals since childhood. Although they love their partners they are prone to addictions or extra-marital affairs. These traits cause problems in family and social life.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Health: Health remains normally good but natives are prone to paralytic attack especially after 55 years of age. Ashthma is also observed among natives.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Positives: Intelligent, Spiritual, Good Communicator.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Negatives: Quarrelsome, Restless and Aggressive.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Remdies: Praying to Lord Krishna and Lord Shiva<\\/p>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"13","created":"2014-02-02 02:31:14","created_by":"899","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2014-03-06 11:59:41","modified_by":"899","checked_out":"899","checked_out_time":"2014-03-06 11:58:02","publish_up":"2014-02-02 02:31:14","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_author\\":\\"\\",\\"link_author\\":\\"\\",\\"show_create_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_modify_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publish_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_item_navigation\\":\\"\\",\\"show_icons\\":\\"\\",\\"show_print_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_email_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_vote\\":\\"\\",\\"show_hits\\":\\"\\",\\"show_noauth\\":\\"\\",\\"urls_position\\":\\"\\",\\"alternative_readmore\\":\\"\\",\\"article_layout\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publishing_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_article_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_backend\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\":\\"\\"}","version":4,"ordering":"11","metakey":"vishakha nakshatra, nakshatra ruled by guru, 27 nakshatra, nakshatra ruled by jupiter","metadesc":"vishakha nakshatra in vedic astrology","access":"1","hits":"0","metadata":"{\\"robots\\":\\"\\",\\"author\\":\\"\\",\\"rights\\":\\"\\",\\"xreference\\":\\"\\"}","featured":"0","language":"*","xreference":""}', 0);
