(405, 5, 1, '', '2014-03-24 07:10:15', 899, 4562, '6fb37edf0885e0f32808aaf9d0aa88bebe5c21dd', '{"id":5,"asset_id":"88","title":"Guru","alias":"guru","introtext":"<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; When an astrologer starts to read a horoscope the two things he is going to definitely check for is position of <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=7:shani&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109\\">Saturn<\\/a> for bad results and Jupiter for good results. Jupiter is the most benefic planet in a horoscope. Popularly known as guru, it is considered a karaka for wealth, happines and well being. A well placed guru in a horoscope suggests a successful and happy life.<\\/p>\\r\\n","fulltext":"\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Jupiter is one planet which alone in a good position can liberate from all other negative influence of planets. It gives a positive outlook in life, gives a calm personality and pleasing appearance. A strong guru signifies a person who is learned, smart, calm and dignified. Guru gives a firm and unwavering faith in god and provides knowledge of Truth. Knowledge alone can free a soul from the worldy chains that plague the human soul and takes the soul closer to its maker aka The God.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Jupiter maybe the most benefic planet in a horoscope but it does have its share of negative influence like any other planet. People with Guru in a prominent position often are a bit chubby. Guru promotes well being but unfortunately it promotes laziness and gluttony also. Guru cause a person to be fat, chubby and easy going. When there is a crisis at work they maybe the calmest persons in the office but they will leave the proactive work to people with strong <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=3:mangal&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109\\">Mangal<\\/a>. They are the ideal employers and marriage partners but not the most ideal employees. They rarely take up challenges which require them to sweat and they rarely have to drop a sweat to achieve something in life. Connection or Co-tenants like <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=4:buddh&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109\\">Budha<\\/a> and <a href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=6:shukra&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109\\">Shukra<\\/a> can cause all hell to break loose. Such people will go to any lenghts to make their pockets bigger and others people''s pockets smaller.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; All said and done, the benefits of Guru far outweigh its drawbacks. People with a strong guru are kind in nature and wonderful friends and family members. They easily get help from all spheres of life. People who crave for an easy lifestyle should definitely hope for a well placed Guru. Those less unfortunate souls who do not have a good disposition of Guru should make their way up the ladder through sheer hard work and dedication<\\/p>","state":1,"catid":"10","created":"2014-02-01 11:46:31","created_by":"899","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2014-03-24 07:10:15","modified_by":"899","checked_out":"899","checked_out_time":"2014-03-24 07:09:52","publish_up":"2014-02-01 11:46:31","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_author\\":\\"\\",\\"link_author\\