(421, 75, 1, '', '2014-03-24 10:16:35', 899, 6371, '79ef3a974d4b93ba96dabc15ea890bd2bdeb4e23', '{"id":75,"asset_id":249,"title":"Neech Bhanga Raja Yoga","alias":"nbry","introtext":"<p>&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Not much is said about Neecha Bhanga Raja Yoga (NBRY) in traditional Vedic Astrology. It was later propogated by new age astrologers through case studies and experience. However what has largely been observed is there are valid reasons to believe that such yoga occurs in a horoscope. Neecha Bhanga Raja Yoga is best explained by the story &lt;a href=\\"<a href=\\"http:\\/\\/en.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/The_Frog_Prince_\\">http:\\/\\/en.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/The_Frog_Prince_<\\/a>(story)\\" target=\\"_blank\\"&gt;Frog Prince&lt;\\/a&gt; written by Grimm Brothers. Nothing in this world inspires people more then the underdog who fights all odds and wins. Rags to Riches story is an inspiration for all people who dream of similar fate.&amp;nbsp;&lt;\\/p&gt;<br \\/>&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; NBRY in simple terms is a yoga which leads an underdog to perform above average deeds and acts. But for NBRY to occur a fundamental law is that the concerned person has to see humiliation and defeat in early part of life so much so that most of those around him start to question the native''s credentials. But these same humiliations and defeats are slowly but surely building the character of native. He starts to see things differently and sooner or later starts to find the ingredients which make him successful and renowned. Ofcourse to the outsiders who questioned him can never imagine that such a worthless scum could achieve unparalleled success so they merely pass it off as Got Lucky but for the native the story is different. He knows the hard work, sweat, patience and noble intentions he had to cultivate to reach that place among elites. In a way it can be said that the Neecha characteristics of the planet never goes away and such natives inspite of their position in life are always questioned by those around.&amp;nbsp;&lt;\\/p&gt;<br \\/>&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Neecha Bhanga has some rules which are needed for its cancellation of neecha chracteristics. Some primary factors are mentioned below:&lt;\\/p&gt;<br \\/>&lt;ol&gt;<br \\/>&lt;li&gt;Neecha planet occupies the Vishnu Sthana or Laxmi Sthana from the Lagna or Chandra counted as Lagna.&lt;\\/li&gt;<br \\/>&lt;li&gt;One of the co-tenants along with the neecha planet is an uccha planet or lord of the rashi (for eg. Guru in Makara Lagna along with Shani or Mangal as co-tenant)&amp;nbsp;&lt;\\/li&gt;<br \\/>&lt;li&gt;Neecha planet is retrograde (for eg. Retrograde Budh in Meena produces NBRY if Guru is located in Karka and native has Meena Lagna).&amp;nbsp;&lt;\\/li&gt;<br \\/>&lt;li&gt;If the ruler of rashi of neecha planet is in kendra and in an uccha sthana or own rashi &amp;nbsp;(for eg. Shani in Mesha would cause neecha bhanga if Mangal is in Makara)&lt;\\/li&gt;<br \\/>&lt;li&gt;If the neecha planet is located in an uccha navamsha in Vishnu or Laxmi Sthana&lt;\\/li&gt;<br \\/>&lt;li&gt;If the neecha planet has good Ashtvarga strength.&lt;\\/li&gt;<br \\/>&lt;\\/ol&gt;<br \\/>&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;These are rough points and really there is actually a lot more to the equation. The term ''Neecha Bhanga'' actually differs from the term ''NBRY''. Neecha Bhanga is just the cancellation of neecha characteristics. In other words Neecha Bhanga leads person to lead a normal or above normal existence but does not have the capacity to turn a beggar into a king. Many people see Neecha Bhanga in their life cause one of the above equations is possible to be present in the horoscope. But NBRY has that capacity to turn dirt into gold. That rarely happens in my humble opinion.&amp;nbsp;&lt;\\/p&gt;<br \\/>&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;One way to know about NBRY is to check the above mentioned points for NBRY particularly the first four points, Afterwards try to honestly answer if you have found your higher purpose in life. As crazy as it sounds people with NBRY tend to live a life devoted to a fixed purpose and that purpose generally involves well-being of others. So if you are still restricted to personal well-being you are not ready to get the NBRY in your horoscope even if present. After all it is not easy to care for others who hurt you and make fun of you. When you learn to accept criticism with dignity and achieve patience, hope, faith and humility is the time when NBRY gives full fruit. More important then that is your purpose to do something in life which would benefit others. At that time even the Gods would bend down and give respect so how can planets be an exception.&amp;nbsp;&lt;\\/p&gt;<br \\/>&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;\\/p&gt;<br \\/>&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;\\/p&gt;<\\/p>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"14","created":"2014-03-24 11:16:05","created_by":"899","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2014-03-24 10:16:35","modified_by":"899","checked_out":"899","checked_out_time":"2014-03-24 10:16:05","publish_up":"2014-03-24 10:16:35","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_author\\":\\"\\",\\"link_author\\":\\"\\",\\"show_create_date\\":\\"\\",\\"