(438, 79, 1, '', '2014-03-24 10:35:19', 899, 4681, '9f5c927bdc4bfd087457b059e33375ab76c46b15', '{"id":79,"asset_id":257,"title":"Ruchaka Yoga","alias":"ruchaka","introtext":"<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Ruchaka Yoga (RY) is part of the Panch Mahapurusha Yoga. Ruchaka Yoga is formed when <a title=\\"Mangala Article Link\\" href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=3:mangal&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109\\">Mangala<\\/a> in in uccha rashi or swakshetra in a <a title=\\"Vishnu Sthana Link\\" href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=72:kendra-stahanas&amp;catid=41:main-articles\\">Vishnu Sthana<\\/a>. In simpler terms it can only happen in (<a title=\\"Mesha Rashi Link\\" href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=22:mesha&amp;catid=11:12-signs&amp;Itemid=111\\">Mesha Rashi<\\/a>, <a title=\\"Vrischika Rashi Link\\" href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=29:vrischika&amp;catid=11:12-signs&amp;Itemid=111\\">Vrischika Rashi<\\/a> and <a title=\\"Makara Rashi Link\\" href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=31:makara&amp;catid=11:12-signs&amp;Itemid=111\\">Makara Rashi<\\/a>) and only when Mangala occupies the 1st house, 4th house, 7th house of 10th house in a horoscope. Some texts mention Ruchaka Yoga can also be counted from Chandra Lagna but it won''t be covered in this article.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Ruchaka Yoga natives are not rare as Mangala gochara transit through horoscope is relatively faster. What is rare is Ruchaka showing its power as one of the Maha Raja Yogas. When it shows the concerned native gets fame as a great warrior, victorious commander\\/army general or even as a superstar in cinemas. Many famous actors and actress are bestowed with this yoga. There are ways like bad placement &nbsp;of Mangala in Navamsha or accompanying enemy planets which can dull the effects of this yoga.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Ruchaka Yoga (RY) effects are as follows. RY natives beget health, wealth and valor. They can achieve high position in police, army or in entertainment industry. They enjoy unparalleled fame and popularity. Sometimes they are more popular than their bosses or Politicos. There is a downside to Ruchaka Yoga in that they can''t be successful in areas like Politics, Diplomacy or Negotiations. They are born to be fighters and do not know the art of tact and deceit. Period of Mangala is extremely beneficial to Ruchaka Yoga natives.&nbsp;According to some texts Ruchaka Yoga natives earn lands and houses and riches. They are blessed with wife and children who are healthy and wealthy. There is a great rapport with siblings and they are successful in agriculture and horticulture.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;When you judge Ruchaka Yoga be sure to know there is no affliction or bad aspect\\/drishti on Mangal. RY gives wonderful results if placed alone in a horoscope or with impressionable planets like Budh and Chandra. It is the one of the rare yogas which can give you fame which can last through ages.<\\/p>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"14","created":"2014-03-24 11:33:42","created_by":"899","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2014-03-24 10:35:19","modified_by":"899","checked_out":"899","checked_out_time":"2014-03-24 10:33:42","publish_up":"2014-03-24 10:35:19","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_author\\":\\"\\",\\"link_author\\":\\"\\",\\"show_create_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_modify_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publish_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_item_navigation\\":\\"\\",\\"show_icons\\":\\"\\",\\"show_print_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_email_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_vote\\":\\"\\",\\"show_hits\\":\\"\\",\\"show_noauth\\":\\"\\",\\"urls_position\\":\\"\\",\\"alternative_readmore\\":\\"\\",\\"article_layout\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publishing_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_article_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_backend\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\":\\"\\"}","version":2,"ordering":"0","metakey":"ruchaka yoga, panch mahapurusha yoga, mars in exaltion, mangal in swakshetra, mangal in uccha rashi","metadesc":"ruchaka yoga description","access":"1","hits":"0","metadata":"{\\"robots\\":\\"\\",\\"author\\":\\"\\",\\"rights\\":\\"\\",\\"xreference\\":\\"\\"}","featured":"0","language":"*","xreference":""}', 0),
