(467, 82, 1, '', '2014-03-25 11:20:09', 899, 4742, 'b7d4bcc9a025e75e84a909e008bff6c644c73f6b', '{"id":82,"asset_id":"269","title":"Bhadra Yoga","alias":"bhadra","introtext":"<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Bhadra Yoga is formed when Budh occupies the <a title=\\"Vishnu Sthana Links\\" href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=72:kendra-stahanas&amp;catid=41:main-articles\\">Vishnu Sthanas<\\/a> and is located in Uccha Rashi or Swakshetra. In simpler terms it can only happen in 1st house, 4th house, 7th house or 10th house and if Budh is located in Mithuna Rashi or Kanya Rashi. Bhadra Yoga is one of yogas which forms the Panch Mahapurusha Yoga (PMY). Compared to other PMY yogas the effects are slightly less as Budh is an impressionable graha and staying close to <a title=\\"Surya Article Link\\" href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=1:surya&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109\\">Surya<\\/a> diminishes its effects. If Budh+Surya happens in <a title=\\"Kanya Rashi Link\\" href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=27:kanya&amp;catid=11:12-signs&amp;Itemid=111\\">Kanya Rashi<\\/a> or <a title=\\"Mithuna Rashi Link\\" href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=24:mithuna&amp;catid=11:12-signs&amp;Itemid=111\\">Mithuna Rashi<\\/a> then along with Bhadra Yoga, an additional Budh-Aditya Yoga is formed which promises intelligence, wealth and fame.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Bhadra Yoga natives have well built body and are youthful in looks. Budh is a prince and to some extent these individuals like princely comforts especially if Budh occupies lagna. Budh is the planet which loves to talk articulately and smartely. They are analytical and possess learning of vivid subjects. Though that doesn''t necessarily translate into knowledge. Budh alone in a rashi is quite talkative even though learned it suits better for native to have a planet like <a title=\\"Mangal Article Link\\" href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=3:mangal&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109\\">Mangal<\\/a> (his enemy), <a title=\\"Shani Article link\\" href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=7:shani&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109\\">Shani<\\/a>, <a title=\\"Guru Article Link\\" href=\\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=5:guru&amp;catid=9:9-planets&amp;Itemid=109\\">Guru<\\/a> or Surya with it. They give direction to the articulate and talkative Budh.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Natives born with Bhadra Yoga are strong, have well developed face and chest, youthful in appearance and brave like a lion. They are ambitious and progressive. They get on quite well with relatives and are always eager to help relatives. They are progressive and innovative and capable of breakthrough in scientific fields if other grahas are suitable. Progress comes gradually for the native.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Though Bhadra yoga is quite good yoga it is even better if one of the above mentioned grahas combines with Budh in rashi of Budh. That would give better results as compared to Budh alone in own rashi in Vishnu Sthanas. &nbsp;<\\/p>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"14","created":"2014-03-25 12:18:52","created_by":"899","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2014-03-25 11:20:09","modified_by":"899","checked_out":"899","checked_out_time":"2014-03-25 11:19:35","publish_up":"2014-03-25 11:19:35","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\